Abadepite bo mu gihugu cya Wales bagaragaje impungenge ko bashobora gufatwa nk'ibimasa.
Bamwe mu bagize inteko bagaragaje ko batishimiye igitekerezo cyo guhindura izina ry'umwanya wabo MWP (Umunyamategeko w'igihugu cya Wales).
Iki gitekerezo cyavutse nyuma yo gukora gahunda yo guhindura izina ry'inteko ishinga amategeko ya Wales.
Abagize Inteko Ishinga Amategeko bahangayikishijwe n'uko iyo gahunda ishobora gutuma abantu babannyega.
Umwe mu bagize ishyaka ry'abakozi mu nama yagize ati "mu cyongereza, iri zina rishya rifite imvugo ijyanye n'amagambo Twp na Pwp".
Niba uturuka hanze ya Pays de Galles: mu rurimi rw'Icyongereza twp bisobanura inozoa na pwp bisobanura kaka.
Ku ruhande rwe, umwe mu bagize inteko ishinga amategeko ya Scotland yavuze ko itsinda ryose "ritanyuzwe cyane" kandi ko ryasabye ko hashakwa andi mazina.
Mu gihe hari undi muyoboke w'ishyaka rya Conservative Party muri Wales wavuze ko yiteguye ibitekerezo bishya byo guhindura izina, ariko nanone yagaragaje impungenge ze ku bisigo bishobora guterwa n'ihinduka rya MWP.
Kugira ngo dusobanukirwe neza uko amakimbirane ari, tugomba kuzirikana ko inyuguti w yo muri Wales n'inyuguti u yo muri Yorkshire mu rurimi rw'icyongereza zifite imvugo isa.
Ku rundi ruhande, komisiyo y'inteko, iri gukora inyandiko y'amategeko yo guhindura amazina, yavuze ibi bikurikira: Ku bijyanye n'abagize Inteko, bazaba bafite inshingano yonyine yo guhitamo ibisobanuro bashaka gukoresha.
Amategeko ya leta ya Wales yo mu 2017 aha inama y'igihugu cya Wales ububasha bwo guhindura izina ryayo.
Muri Kamena, Komisiyo yasohoye ibisubizo by'ubushakashatsi bwa rubanda mu guhitamo ibyifuzo byatanzwe, kandi muri rusange izina Inteko Ishinga Amategeko ya Wales ryitabiriwe n'amagambo menshi yo kwishyira hamwe.
Ku bijyanye n'amazina y'abagize inteko, Komisiyo yahisemo izina ry'Abadepite b'Abadepite b'i Wales cyangwa WMP (mu mpfunyapfunyo z'icyongereza), ariko izina rya MWP ryatoranyijwe mu matora y'abaturage.
Abadepite batanga ibitekerezo bitandukanye, ariko biragoye cyane guhitamo kimwe mu byemezo by'amajwi, cyane cyane kuri Perezida w'Inteko, Elin Jones, washatse ko mu byumweru bike yoherereza inyandiko y'ibyahindutse.
Ariko, amategeko azagira ingaruka ku mikorere y'inama; mu byo bizakorwa harimo amategeko yo kwirinda ibikorwa byashoboraga guteza abanyamuryango b'inama guhomba kandi igishushanyo cy'urwego rw'inama kizakemurwa hifashishijwe itegeko.
Mu gihe hazaba hari ibiganiro ku ivugururwa ry'itegeko, abagize Inteko bazahabwa umwanya wo gufata umwanzuro ku byerekeye amazina yabo.
