Abaturage bazagira amajwi ku cyumweru niba izina ry'igihugu ryahindurwa rikaba Repubulika ya Macédoine y'Amajyaruguru.
Iri huriro ryashyizweho mu rwego rwo gushaka uko habaho ubwumvikane hagati y'u Bugereki n'igihugu cya Macedonia.
Leta ya Atene imaze igihe kirekire ivuga ko izina ry'umuturanyi wayo wo mu majyaruguru ari uburenganzira bw'ubutaka bwayo, kandi yagiye ihangana n'ibyifuzo by'ibihugu byo kwinjira mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi no mu muryango wa OTAN.
Perezida wa Macedonia, Gjorge Ivanov, uhatanira kuyobora amatora yo guhindura izina rye, yavuze ko atazibagirwa uko amatora azaba.
Ariko, abashigikiye referendumu (harimo Minisitiri w'Intebe Zoran Zaev) bavuga ko ari igiciro cyo kwinjira mu Bwongereza no muri NATO.
Inzogera z'urusengero rwa St. Martin zagiye zitakaza imbaraga kubera ibibazo by'amatorero yo muri Harlem.
"Naganiriye n'abantu bakuru, bavuga ko mu myaka yashize, ku mahuriro y'imihanda hari utubari n'insengero", ni ko Bwana Adams avuga.
Ariko ubu nta kintu na kimwe kiriho.
Avuga ko nta kibazo cyo kubura mu tubari.
