Ibibuga by'imyidagaduro ntibikiri amazu y'abaturanyi abantu bahuriragaho
Ku byerekeye Kiliziya, hari impungenge ko amafaranga azaturuka mu kugurisha umutungo wacu atazaba ahagije, kandi ko mbere cyangwa nyuma y'igihe runaka, tuzasubira aho twatangiriye.
Nanone, insengero zishobora gusimburwa n'amazu y'amacumbi, kandi amazu y'amacumbi yuzuyemo abantu batita ku nsengero z'abaturanyi babo.
Ati "Abantu bazagura amazu y'abaturage bazaba ari abazungu". Avuga ko ari yo mpamvu insengero zizapfa zifunze mu kanya gato kuko abo bantu bashya atari abayoboke b'amatorero.
Amatorero yombi yubatswe n'amatorero y'abazungu mbere yuko Harlem iba umujyi w'abirabura; yabaye Umuryango wa Metropolitan mu 1870, hanyuma San Martin yubakwa nyuma y'imyaka icumi.
Itorero rya Methodiste ry'umwimerere ryahise riva muri aka gace mu 1930.
Nyuma yaho, itsinda ry'abirabura ryaje gufata umwanya w'umukuru w'igihugu.
Itorero ry'abirabura rya Reverend John Howard Johnson ryafashe Itorero rya St. Martin; Howard yateguye boycott ku maduka yo mu mihanda 125 y'ubucuruzi ya Harlem atemeraga abakozi b'abirabura cyangwa ngo abafashe.
Mu 1939 igitero cy'inkongi cyangiritse cyane, ariko abayoboke ba padiri Johnson bakoze gahunda zitandukanye zo kubaka itorero no gutumiza ingoma.
Reverend David Johnson, umuhungu wa Padiri Johnson akaba n'umuragwa wa San Martin, yise iyo karuneri "Inzogera y'abakene".
Mu kwezi kwa karindwi, umuhanga mu gucuranga impanda yamwise "Ubutunzi bw'umuco" na "Ikintu cy'amateka kidashobora gusimburwa".
Umuhanga mu by'imyidagaduro, Tiffany Nek wo muri kaminuza ya Michigan, yavuze ko iyi ari yo karuneri ya mbere ku isi yakoreshejwe n'umuhanzi w'umwirabura, Dionisio A. Lind, wari waragiye mu rusengero rwa Riverside mu myaka 18 ishize, aho yakoresheje karuneri nini.
Bwana Merriweather yasobanuye ko St. Martin itasimbuye abahanzi bayo.
Mu mezi ashize, San Martin yabonye urugendo rurerure rw'abahanga mu by'ubwubatsi n'abakozi, bamwe muri bo bazanwe n'abayobozi b'abanyamahanga cyangwa diyosezi ya episkopi.
Inama y'abapadiri (inama y'ubuhanzi igizwe n'abayobozi b'abanyamahanga), ku rundi ruhande, yoherereje diyosezi ibaruwa muri Nyakanga yo kwemeza ko "igiciro cyakozwe" n'ishoramari ry'abo bantu "kizajya kuri paruwasi", kuko paruwasi idafite aho ihuriye n'ishoramari ry'abahanga mu by'ubwubatsi n'abakozi batumweko na diyosezi.
Hari abanyamadini batandukanye batanze ibirego ku kutabona ibintu mu buryo bweruye muri diyosezi.
