Imigambi ya Sainsbury's yo kwinjira mu isoko ry'imirimbo yo mu Bwongereza
Supermarket Sainsbury's yateye imbere mu maduka nka Boots, Superdrug na Debenhams ubu ikaba ifite urwego rw'ubwiza mu buryo bw'amaduka akomeye, rufite abakozi benshi kandi b'abahanga.
Mu gihe ibicuruzwa by'imideli n'ibikoresho byo mu rugo bigenda bigabanuka, miliyari 2.8 z'amapawundi zashyizwe mu bucuruzi bw'ubwiza mu Bwongereza, buzamuka butagira imipaka; hazabakwa ibice binini by'ubucuruzi bw'ubwiza, bizageragezwa mu maduka 11 yo hirya no hino mu gihugu. Niba ibicuruzwa byavuyemo umusaruro mwiza, andi maduka azafungurwa mu mwaka utaha.
Ubucuruzi bw'ubwiza butuma amaduka manini ashobora kugura televiziyo, microwaves n'ibindi bikoresho byo mu rugo.
Nkuko byatangajwe n'amasupamaketi ya Sainsburys, ibicuruzwa byabo by'ubwiza bizikuba kabiri ndetse bitange ibicuruzwa birenga 3000; bizanagaragaramo Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman na Dr. PawPaw ndetse n'ibindi biranga nk'ibyo ku bakiriya.
Ku bijyanye n'ibyamamare nka L'Oreal, Maybelline na Burt's Bees, bazaba bafite umwanya mwinshi mu bice by'ibyamamare nk'ibyo ushobora gusanga mu maduka ya Boots.
Byongeye kandi, isoko rikora ibirungo ryongeye gushyira ahagaragara ibirungo byayo Boutique, ari igicuruzwa cya vegan gusa; abakiriya bato barushaho gusaba ibicuruzwa nkibi.
Ikigo cy'ubucuruzi bw'ibinyobwa cya Fragrance Shop kizajya kigerageza ibiciro byacyo mu maduka abiri ya Sainsbury's, icya mbere cyafunguwe mu cyumweru gishize mu mujyi wa Croydon mu majyepfo y'umujyi wa Londres, naho icya kabiri kizaba cyuguruwe mu mpera z'uyu mwaka mu mujyi wa Birmingham.
Kubera kugura ibintu kuri interineti no kugura buri munsi mu maduka mato yo hafi aho, amaduka akomeye agomba gukora cyane kugira ngo akomeze kubona abakiriya.
Mike Coupe, umuyobozi mukuru w'amaduka manini ya Sainsbury's, yavuze ko amaduka manini azagenda agendera ku buryo bwo gucuruza mu maduka manini, kandi ko uru ruganda rw'amaduka manini ruzagabanya akaga gakomeye kagerwaho n'abarushanwa na Aldi na Lidl, binyuze mu gutanga serivisi nyinshi n'ibindi bicuruzwa bitari ibyo kurya.
Isupamaketi ya Sainsbury's yafunguye ibigo by'ubucuruzi bya Argos mu maduka abarirwa mu magana ndetse ifunguye ibigo bitandukanye bya Habitats, nyuma yo kugurwa n'izo nzego zombi mu myaka ibiri ishize; kubera ko ibicuruzwa by'ibiribwa byongerewe imbaraga kandi inzego zaguze zirunguka kurusha mbere.
Muri icyo gihe, isoko ryagerageje kongera gufungura, icyiciro cy'imiti n'imirimbo, ariko iyo gahunda ntiyagenze neza.
Nyuma yaho, Sainsbury's Boots yashyize hamwe mu ntangiriro za 2000, ariko ubu bufatanye bwarangiye kuko inzira yo gusaranganya inyungu mu byiciro by'imiti byo mu masupamaketi yabaye impapuro zishe.
Ubu buryo bushya bwashyizweho igihe isoko rikuru rya Sainsbury's ryagurishaga ibicuruzwa by'imiti mu maduka 281 ryagombaga kugurisha Celesio, nyiri urubuga rwa Lloyds Pharmacy, ku mafaranga miliyoni 125 mu myaka itatu ishize.
Uruganda rwa Lloyds ruzaba rufite uruhare muri gahunda iteganijwe: ruzongera urusobe runini rw'ibimenyetso by'ubwiza mu bucuruzi bune; harimo La Roche-Posay na Vichy.
Paul Mills-Hicks, umuyobozi ushinzwe ubucuruzi mu masoko akomeye ya Sainsbury's yagize ati "Twongeye gushimangira isura y'ibiro by'ububanyi n'amahanga by'ubwiza kugira ngo abakiriya bacu babone ahantu heza cyane.
Nanone kandi, twashyize abakozi b'inararibonye mu kazi kugira ngo baduhe inama ku birebana n'ibicuruzwa.
Twashyizeho urutonde rwacu rwo guhanga kugirango tubashe guhuza ibyifuzo byose kandi, kubera ibidukikije byiza n'ahantu heza, ibigo byacu byubwiza bitanga uburyo bugezweho kandi bworoshye bwo guhangana n'amaduka akoresha uburyo bwa kera.
Peter Jones "yarakajwe n'uko Holly Willoughby yanze gutanga miliyoni 11 z'amapawundi
Peter Jones, umukinnyi wa filime yitwa "Dragons Den" yitabye Imana "afite uburakari" nyuma y'uko Holly Willoughby, umuyobozi wa televiziyo, yateye utwatsi amasezerano y'amapawundi miliyoni 11 yari afitanye isano n'ubucuruzi bw'icyo kinyamakuru, kugira ngo ashobore kwibanda ku masezerano mashya afitanye na Marks and Spencer na ITV.
Willoughby nta gihe afite cyo kurya ibintu byo mu rugo.
Ubucuruzi bw'aba bombi bwagereranyijwe n'ubw'umwuga wa Gwyneth Paltrow.
Uyu mugabo w'imyaka 37 utanga ibiganiro bya This Morning, yakoresheje Instagram mu gutangaza ko yeguye.
Nyuma y'aho Holly Willoughby asezeye mu kazi kugira ngo yemere amasezerano yari yatanzwe na Marks & Spencer na ITV, Peter Jones, umuhanzi w'icyamamare muri Dragons, yarakajwe cyane no kuba yaretse ubucuruzi bw'inyungu bari barashyizeho ku munota wa nyuma.
Amakuru dukesha iyi nkuru avuga ko hari inama yari iherutse kuba ku wa Kabiri w'icyumweru gishize mu biro bikuru bya Marlow, aho Jones yari "yarakaye cyane" ubwo yumvaga umugore w'icyamamare muri televiziyo avuga ko agiye kwemera amasezerano mashya y'amapawundi miliyoni 1,5 bityo akaba atazongera kubona umwanya wo kwita ku bikoresho byo mu rugo by'umwuga.
Ubu bucuruzi bwagereranyijwe n'ubundi bwa Gwyneth Paltrow bwitwa Goop, kandi bwikubye kabiri umutungo wa Willoughby wa miriyoni 11 z'amapawundi.
Nyuma y'aho Willoughby w'imyaka 37 aherukiye gutangaza kuri Instagram ko agiye kuva mu bucuruzi bw'ikimenyetso cya Truly, Jones yavuye mu Bwongereza ajya mu nzu y'ibiruhuko.
Hari amakuru avuga ko icyo kintu cyari mu bintu Holly yashyiraga mu mwanya wa mbere.
Ni umwanzuro uzatuma imyaka 20 iri imbere imubera myiza.
Icyakora, umwanzuro wafashe wo gushyiraho ikimenyetso waradutunguye.
Nta muntu n'umwe wari wemera ibyabaye ku wa Kabiri w'icyumweru gishize, ubwo icyo kigo cyari kigiye gusohora igicuruzwa cyacyo.
Byongeye kandi, ubu inzu y'ubutabazi yo mu kigo cy'ababyeyi cya Marlow yuzuye ibicuruzwa by'agaciro kenshi.
Nk'uko impuguke zivuga, isosiyete iri hafi gutakaza miliyoni z'amapawundi kubera kuva kwa This Morning (ni we muhanzi ufite inyungu nyinshi mu Bwongereza); isosiyete yashyize amafaranga menshi mu bicuruzwa bitandukanye (harimo imyenda, buji, imyenda n'ibikoresho byo mu rugo) kandi ubu igomba guhangana n'ibihombo bishobora kuvuka.
Uretse n'ibyo, iyo abantu batavuga rumwe, bishobora gutuma ubucuti bwabo buhagarara.
Willoughby n'umugabo we Dan Baldwin bafite abana batatu, kandi Jones n'umugore we Tara Capp, bamaze imyaka icumi ari inshuti magara.
Willoughby na Capp bashinze uruganda rwa Truly mu 2016 naho Jones w'imyaka 52 yinjiye mu buyobozi muri Werurwe.
Aba bombi bakunda gutegura gahunda zabo z'ikiruhuko hamwe kandi Jones afite 40% by'ikigo cya Baldwin cyo gutunganya ibiganiro bya televiziyo.
Willoughby azasimbura Ant McPartlin mu kiganiro cya I'm A Celebrity kuri ITV.
Amakuru aturuka mu kigo cya Jones yavuze ko ejo bundi, "Kick Jones atazagira icyo avuga ku bikorwa bye by'ubucuruzi".
Twarakomeje tuganira, ariko nyuma yaho twarakundanye.
Yarasetse avuga ku byo yatutswe n'itangazamakuru, byose avuga ko ari "amagambo mabi" ku muyobozi wa Koreya ya Ruguru.
Kuki Perezida Trump atanga ibintu byinshi?
Trump yakoresheje ijwi rye rya "TV" mu gusubiza amagambo y'urwenya:
"Nta cyo ntanze".
Nyuma y'inama ya mbere yabereye i Singapore muri Kamena, Perezida Trump yavuze ko Kim yifuzaga guterana ubwa kabiri, bityo bikaba ari intambwe ikomeye mu nzira yo gukuraho intwaro za kirimbuzi muri Koreya ya Ruguru.
Ariko kandi, gahunda yo gukuraho intwaro za kirimbuzi iracyari mu kirere.
Nyuma y'amezi atatu gusa habaye inama i Singapour muri Kamena, umuyobozi wa Koreya ya Ruguru, Ri Yong Ho, yabwiye abayobozi b'isi muri Loni ati: "Mu nama rusange yabaye ku wa Gatandatu, Koreya ya Ruguru ntiyabonye "igisubizo gihagije" kivuye muri Amerika ku byemezo by'igihugu ku nzira yo guhagarika intwaro za kirimbuzi".
Ahubwo, Amerika yashyizeho ibihano bikomeye kugira ngo ikomeze kubikoresha.
Trump we afite icyizere, kandi yabigaragaje mu ijambo rye rya nyuma.
Yagize ati "Ubucuti dufitanye na Koreya ya Ruguru buri ku rwego rwo hejuru kurusha mbere hose".
Byongeye kandi, twari hafi gutangiza intambara na Koreya ya Ruguru.
Iyo ntambara ishobora guhitana abantu babarirwa muri za miriyoni.
Ariko ubu dufitanye umubano udasanzwe".
Yongeyeho ko imihati yashyizweho yo kunoza umubano na Kim yazanye umusaruro mwiza; harimo ko igerageza rya misile ryarangiye, inzira zo kurekura imfungwa zarushijeho kunozwa kandi ko gusubika izindi ngabo za Amerika biri mu nzira.
Nanone kandi, bigaragaza uko yabonaga ibintu mu buryo butari bwo mu biganiro yagiranye na Kim.
"Ni akazi koroshye cyane kuba perezida, ariko aho kugira abantu 10.000 bagerageza kwinjira mu gihugu ku ngufu, dufite abantu 200 hano", Trump yavuze mu gihe yerekezaga ku bantu bari aho.
Umutingito n'umutingito byateje tsunami mu kirwa cya Indoneziya, bihitana abantu babarirwa mu magana
Nyuma y'umutingito wa Lombok, urugero, ubufasha bw'imiryango mpuzamahanga idaharanira inyungu ntibukenewe.
Nubwo abaturage bagera kuri 10% bo mu gihugu cya Lombok bavuye mu byabo, umutingito ntiwatangajwe nk'ibiza ku rwego rw'igihugu (ni ikintu cy'ibanze mu gusaba ubufasha bw'amahanga).
"Mu bihe byinshi, ikibabaje ni uko leta yavuze ko idakeneye ubufasha mpuzamahanga, bityo iki ni ikibazo gikomeye", niko Madamu Sumbung avuga.
Umuryango Save the Children urimo gushyira hamwe itsinda ryo kujya muri Palou, ariko ntaramenya niba abitangiye gukora imirimo bashobora gukorera muri icyo gihugu.
Bwana Sutopo, uhagarariye ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe guhangana n'ibiza, yatubwiye ko abayobozi ba Indoneziya barimo gukora ku buryo ubufasha bw'amahanga bwemerwa.
Nubwo Indoneziya yagiye ihura n'imitingito myinshi, icyo gihugu cyafashe ingamba zikomeye zo guhangana n'ibiza.
Inkuta z'ibikoresho bya tsunami zubatse muri Aceh, ariko haracyariho inkike nke cyane ku nkombe.
Palu nta cyuma cyo kuburira abantu afite. Iyo cyuma cy'umuburo gikora, bishobora kuba ari byo byatumye hapfa abantu benshi.
Iyo ikirere ari cyiza, gutembera hagati y'ibirwa bya Indoneziya bishobora kuba ikibazo.
Ikindi kandi, ibiza by'ibidukikije bituma gushyira mu bikorwa ibikorwa by'ibikoresho bigoye.
Ubwato bw'ibitaro bufasha abazahajwe n'umutingito bwahagaze i Lombok, ubu bujya i Palua, ariko buzafata iminsi itatu ngo bugere aho habaye impanuka.
Iterambere rya Perezida Joko Widodo ryibandaga ku bikorwa byo kunoza ibikorwa remezo bya Indoneziya kandi yashyize amafaranga menshi mu kunoza imihanda n'imihanda ya gari ya moshi.
Ariko kandi, amafaranga y'igihugu yagabanutse, kandi ubuyobozi bwa Perezida Joko bugomba guhangana n'ibibazo mu gihe bitegura amatora y'umukuru w'igihugu umwaka utaha.
Bwana Joko na we afite ibibazo byo kugenzura amakimbirane y'amadini muri Indoneziya, urugero, abenshi mu bagize ishyaka rya Islam bahindutse abagendera ku mahame y'idini.
Ibi byatumye abantu barenga 1000 bapfa, abandi ibihumbi mirongo batakaza amazu yabo, kubera ko imitwe y'aba-Kristo n'abayisilamu yagiye ijya mu mihanda, ikoresha ibyuma birimo imbugita, imyambi, imyambi n'ibindi.
Reba umukino wa nyuma wa Liverpool na Chelsea
Igitego cya Daniel Sturridge ku munota wa 89 ku mukino wa Stamford Bridge i Londres ku wa Gatandatu, cyatumye Liverpool irokoka umukino wa Premier League yari yatakaje na Chelsea.
Nyuma yo guhererekanya umupira kuri metero 30 kuri Chealsea, Sturridge yabonye uburyo bwo guhindura igitego 1-0.
Mbere y'uko asunika umupira ku nkingi y'irembo, yawushyize ibumoso bwe.
Icyo gitego cyatumye umupira uguruka ugana mu mucanga, ugahita ugera hejuru iburyo bw'urushundura.
