Ingurube yishe umuhinzi w'Umushinwa
Umworozi yishwe n'ingurube mu isoko ryo mu majyepfo ashyira uburengerazuba bw'u Bushinwa, nkuko bitangazwa n'ibinyamakuru byo muri ako gace.
Umugabo witwa "Yuan" yishwe asanga umubiri we ufite umutsi w'amaraso wose, mu kigo cy'ingurube kiri ku isoko rya Liupanshu mu ntara ya Guizhou, nkuko ikinyamakuru South China Morning Post cyabitangaje ku cyumweru.
Ku itariki ya 30 Gicurasi 2005, umworozi w'ingurube yitegura gutera abarwayi bo mu bwoko bw'ingurube, mu ntara ya Qinghai mu Bushinwa.
Mu minsi ya gatatu, ajya mu isoko rya Yunnan n'umuvandimwe we, bagurisha ingurube 15.
Mu gitondo cyakurikiyeho, mubyara we yaje kubona umurambo we, abona ko urugi rw'urugo rw'ingurube rwo hafi aho rwari rufunguye.
Nanone yavuze ko mu rugo rw'ingurube hari ingurube nini ifite amaraso mu kanwa.
Raporo y'iperereza ry'ubugenzacyaha yemeje ko iyo ngurube y'amapawundi 550 ari yo yishe uwo muhinzi.
"Ibirenge bya mubyara wanjye byari byuzuye amaraso kandi byari byarabaye ibikomere"
Nk'uko bigaragara mu mashusho ya kamera, Yuan ashobora kugaragara yinjira mu isoko saa kumi n'ebyiri n'iminota 40 za mu gitondo cyo kuwa kane agiye kugaburira ingurube.
Umurambo we wabonetse nyuma y'isaha.
Inyamaswa yishe uwo mugabo ntiyari iy'umwuzukuru we Yuan cyangwa mwene se wabo.
Nk'uko umuyobozi w'isoko yabwiye Evening News, iyo ngurube iri mu nzu kugira ngo irinde ibindi bikorwa byo kuyitera, bityo abapolisi bashobore kubona ibimenyetso.
Umuryango wa Yuan n'abayobozi b'isoko barimo baragirana ibiganiro ku byerekeye indishyi z'akababaro z'urupfu rwe.
Nubwo ibyo ari ibintu bidasanzwe, hari izindi nkuru zavuze iby'ibitero by'ingurube.
Mu mwaka wa 2016, ingurube yateye umugore n'umugabo we mu isambu yo muri Massachusetts, umugabo arakomereka bikomeye.
Imyaka icumi mbere yaho, ingurube y'amapawundi 650 yari yarashyize muri gari ya moshi y'umuhinzi wo mu gihugu cya Galles, kugeza ubwo umugore w'uwo mugabo yamwirukanye.
Mu 2012, umuhinzi wo muri Oregon yaraye arye ingurube, nyuma yaho umuhinzi wo muri Manitoba yavuze mu makuru ya CBC News ko ingurube zitari inyamaswa z'inkazi, ariko ko iyo zinywereye amaraso, zishobora kuba zanduza.
