Abahanga mu by'ubumenyi bw'isi bagaragaje ko uwo muriro w'ibirunga uri ku birometero 72 mu majyepfo y'uburasirazuba bw'umurwa mukuru wa Mexico, wiyongereye cyane kuva umutingito wari ufite ubukana bwa 7,1 wibasiye akarere ko hagati muri Mexico muri Nzeri 2017.
Iki kirunga cyitwa Don Goyo, cyaratangiye gukora mu 1994.
Imirwano hagati ya polisi n'abashaka kwigenga muri Catalogne mbere y'umunsi wo kwibuka amatora yo kwibohora
Abantu batandatu batawe muri yombi kuri uyu wa Gatandatu i Barcelona kubera imirwano hagati y'abari mu myigaragambyo y'ubwigenge n'abapolisi mu gihe ibihumbi by'abantu bari mu myigaragambyo yo kwibuka isabukuru ya mbere y'amatora yo kwibohora muri Catalonia.
Abapolisi bari bashinzwe kurwanya imvururu bahagaritse itsinda ry'abashaka kwigenga bari bambaye ubusa, ariko babatera amagi n'ibishashi by'amabara, bituma imihanda yari yuzuye ba mukerarugendo ihinduka ibicu by'umukungugu.
Nyuma yaho, habaye imyigaragambyo myinshi kubera ko abapolisi bakoreshaga inkoni zabo mu guhosha imvururu.
Mu gihe cy'amasaha menshi, amatsinda y'abashaka ubwigenge yarasesekaye aririmba ati "Ntabwo tuzibagirwa, ntabwo tuzababarira" imbere y'abashyigikiye ubwigenge, baririmba bati "Humure Espagne".
Amakuru dukesha itangazamakuru ryaho avuga ko abantu 14 bavurwa ibikomere byoroheje bakomerekejwe n'imvururu.
Hari ubwoba bwinshi muri ako karere ka Catalogne, kagerageza kwibohora nyuma y'amatora yabaye ku wa 1 Ukwakira, avuga ko atari amategeko, ariko ko abatavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi muri Catalogne bashoboye kubona umunsi wo kuyihimbaza.
Abenshi mu batoye batoye ubwigenge, ariko ubwitabire bw'abaturage bwari buke cyane kubera umubare munini w'abaturage barwanya ubwigenge bashakaga kwamagana amatora.
Abategetsi ba Catalogne bavuga ko abantu 1000 bakomeretse nyuma y'igitero cy'abapolisi bari bagiye ku biro by'itora kugira ngo bahagarike abahitamo, bituma habaho imvururu.
Mu minsi ishize, amatsinda y'abashaka ubwigenge yari acumbitse mu nkambi yo mu mujyi wa New York, mu rwego rwo kwirinda imyigaragambyo y'abavuga ko bashyigikiye polisi y'igihugu.
Bakoze urugendo, ariko bahatiwe guhindura inzira.
Narcis Termes, ufite imyaka 68, ni umunya-amashanyarazi, yajyanye n'umugore we mu myigaragambyo yo kwamagana ubwigenge, avuga ko nta cyizere cy'uko Catalonia izabasha kwigenga.
Mu mwaka ushize twarabanye neza cyane.
Ababyeyi banjye bararize kubera ibyishimo kuko noneho bari bafite uburenganzira bwo gutora, ariko ubu turafunze, " ni ko yavuze.
Nyuma yo gutsinda gato ariko bikomeye mu matora yo mu karere yabaye mu kwezi kwa cumi na kabiri gushize, amashyaka y'abakatalani aharanira ubwigenge yagize ibibazo byinshi muri uyu mwaka byo gukomeza gushimisha abaturage; bamwe mu bayobozi b'amashyaka bari mu buhungiro cyangwa barafunzwe, ubu bategereje kuburanishwa kubera gutunganya referendumu no gutangaza ubwigenge.
Joan Puig, umukanishi w'imyaka 42 y'amavuko, arimo afata amashusho y'imyigaragambyo y'abapolisi kuri telefoni ye, avuga ko abanyapolitiki bo mu mashyaka yombi ari bo bafite uruhare muri ibi.
Yagize ati "Noneho ibintu birushaho kuba bibi".
Kuri uyu wa gatandatu, Oriol Junqueras, umwe mu bayobozi bakomeye ba Catalonia, umaze umwaka afunzwe ategereje urubanza rwe, yatangaje ko azitabira amatora y'abadepite b'u Burayi ateganyijwe mu mwaka utaha.
Ati "Nindamuka nitoreye kuba umukandida mu matora y'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, ni bwo buryo bwiza bwo kwamagana ivangura ry'indangagaciro za demokarasi n'ihohoterwa rikorerwa ubutegetsi bwa Espagne".
