Umugenzuzi Bob Blemmings yavuze ko iyi nzu n'inzugi byangiritse.
Ikindi kandi, biragaragara ko imodoka y'uwo musirikare yakoreshejwe umuheto.
Igitego cya Memba cyatumye Livingston itsinda Rangers igitego 1-0.
Igitego cya mbere cya Dolly Menga cyemeje ko Livingston ari we ufite umwenda munini kurusha abandi
Livingston wari umaze kuzamurwa mu ntera yatangaje abakinnyi ba Rangers, ndetse Steven Gerrard atsindwa ku nshuro ya kabiri mu mikino 18 amaze ayobora Ibrox.
Igitego cya Dolly Menga cyabaye ingenzi mu mukino wa kabiri ubwo ikipe ya Gary Holten yazamukaga mu cyiciro cya kabiri.
Ikipe ya Gerrard nta mukino yatsinze muri shampiyona y'icyiciro cya mbere, bityo izahura n'abakinnyi bayoboye ikipe ya Hearts (bari bafite amanota umunani) ku cyumweru gitaha.
Mbere y'umukino wa nyuma, abakinnyi ba Rangers bazahura na Rapid Vienna mu mukino wa Europa League kuwa kabiri.
Hagati aho, Livingston ifite umukino umwe nta gutsindwa, imikino itandatu isigaye muri uyu mwaka, umutoza Holt ntazi icyo gutsindwa ari cyo kuva yasimbuye Kenny Miller mu kwezi gushize.
Livingston yatakaje amahirwe menshi ku bashyitsi bakomeye.
Ikipe ya Holt yagombaga gufata umwanya mbere yo gutsinda igitego, ariko kubera ubutabera bwe budasanzwe, yateje ibibazo byinshi ikipe ya Rangers.
Scott Robinson yakoze urugendo rwe ariko imbaraga ze zose zarahombye imbere y'urugi, hanyuma Alan Lithgow yongera gushyira imbaraga ze ku rugi nyuma yo gukubitwa umutwe na Craig Halket.
Abashyitsi bari banyuzwe no kureka abakinnyi ba Rangers bakina, ariko bari bazi ko abashyitsi bashoboraga kubagusha igihe icyo ari cyo cyose.
Kandi iyo myumvire ni yo yatumye atsinda igitego cy'ingenzi.
Abakinnyi ba Rangers bahawe igitego cy'umudendezo, Livingston ahita afungura; Declan Gallagher na Robinson bahuza igitego cya Menga, ariko uwo wa nyuma atsinda igitego mu gice cy'imbere cy'izamu.
Muri icyo gihe, ikipe ya Rangers yari ifite ububasha ku kibuga ariko abakinnyi bo mu rugo bari bafite imbaraga nyinshi, maze umunyezamu Liam Kelly abinyuza mu kibuga nta kibazo.
Iyi myenda yakomeje kugeza hagati mu gice cya kabiri, ariko igitego cya Alfredo Morelos cyasabye ubuhanga bwa Kelly.
Scott Pittman ntiyashoboye gutsinda igitego ku mukinnyi wa Rangers kubera umunyezamu Allan McGregor, bityo Lithgowe yirinda igitego cya Livingston.
Ibihano byatanzwe inshuro nyinshi mu mucanga wa Livingston kandi byasohotse inshuro nyinshi n'abakinnyi bo murugo; ibihano bibiri byasabwe, kimwe Halkett kubera guhangana na Glenn Middleton wasimbuye undi kubera ko yakorakora umupira n'ikiganza cye, ariko byombi byaraciwe.
Umukino wa Livingston - isesengura ry'ibitangaje
Alasdair Lamont wo kuri BBC Scotland, Tony Macaroni kuri Arena
Umukino wa Livingston wari mwiza cyane kandi utanga umusaruro mwiza.
Ku bwanjye, bakoze ibintu bitangaje kandi bafite amahirwe menshi yo kuzamurwa mu ntera.
Imikino n'imyitwarire y'ikipe ntibyigeze bihinduka cyane kuva aho bageze mu cyiciro cya mbere, ariko Holt yabaye umutoza udasanzwe, kuva aho ageze yashyize ikipe mu nzira nziza.
Yari afite intwari nyinshi.
Kapiteni Halkett yakoze akazi gakomeye, mu buryo bwo gutegura no gucunga umutekano udasanzwe, kandi Menga yakoze ibishoboka byose kugira ngo Connor Goldson na Joe Worrall bahore bashya ubwoba mu mukino wose.
Ariko kandi, nta kintu na kimwe cyatumaga abahanzi b'abakinnyi b'imikino ngororangingo bagira icyo bakora.
Bakora neza cyane igihe bayobowe na Gerrard, ariko ntibakomeza gukurikiza amahame y'umutoza wabo.
Imikino ya nyuma yabaye mibi cyane, batsinze abakinnyi bo mu rugo rimwe gusa, bityo rero, abakinnyi ba Rangers bagomba kugira icyo bakora vuba niba bashaka kuva hagati mu kibuga.
Erdogan yakiriwe nabi cyane i Cologne
Hari urwenya n'ijuru ry'ubururu ku wa Gatandatu, ubwo abayobozi ba Turukiya n'Abadage bahuriraga i Berlin gufata ifunguro rya mu gitondo.
Ni umunsi wa nyuma w'uruzinduko rwa Perezida Erdogan mu Budage, rwari rushingiye ku mishyikirano myiza hagati y'ibihugu bigize OTAN.
Baganiriye ku bibazo bitandukanye birimo ikibazo cy'uburenganzira bwa muntu n'ubwisanzure bw'itangazamakuru ndetse n'icy'uko Turukiya yakwinjira mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'uburayi.
Hanyuma, Erdogan yagiye i Cologne gufungura urusengero runini.
Niwo mujyi utuwe cyane muri Turukiya hanze ya Turukiya.
Kubera umutekano muke wariho mu gihe cya polisi, abantu 25.000 bari baje mu myigaragambyo imbere ya mosque barahagaritswe, ariko hari benshi mu bayoboke babo bari baje kureba perezida wabo.
Abantu babarirwa mu magana bari mu myigaragambyo yo kwamagana Erdogan (abenshi bari abakurude) bahurije hamwe amajwi yabo bamagana ingamba za Erdogan n'icyemezo cya guverinoma y'Ubudage cyo kwakira perezida.
Abari mu myigaragambyo ku mpande zombi bagaragaje ko Perezida atavuga rumwe n'abaturage b'Abadage bamwe bamwita intwari abandi bamwita umutegetsi w'igitugu.
