Umupira w'amaguru yapfuye ubwo yagonganaga n'imodoka mu mujyi wa Londres.
Iyi mpanuka yabaye ahagana saa kumi n'ebyiri n'iminota 15 z'ijoro, ku muhanda wa Bestwood na Evelyn, mu majyepfo ashyira uburasirazuba bw'umujyi wa Deptford.
Umushoferi yahagaze, imodoka y'ubutabazi irahagera ariko uwo mugabo yahise apfa.
Mu muhanda wa Childers, hafi y'aho impanuka yabaye ku wa Gatandatu, undi mukinnyi w'amagare yapfuye mu kwezi gushize, maze umushoferi ahunga.
