Abapolisi batandatu bakomerekeye mu mirwano muri gereza ya Long Lartin
Abacungagereza batandatu bakomerekeye mu mirwano yabaye muri gereza y'abagabo ifite umutekano wihanitse, nkuko ibiro by'iyo gereza byabitangaje.
Impaka z'abakozi ba gereza ya HMP Long Lartin mu ntara ya Worcestershire zigeze ku isaha ya saa cyenda n'igice z'ijoro ryo ku cyumweru.
Abakozi b'ikigo cy'ubugenzacyaha cy'i Tornado bageze muri gereza kugira ngo bahagarike imvururu zatangijwe n'abantu umunani bafashwe, ubu zikaba ziganjemo igice kimwe cy'inyubako.
Abo basirikare bose bari bafite ibikomere byoroheje ku maso, kandi byarakemutse ako kanya.
Umuyobozi wa gereza yavuze ko hari abakozi b'abagororwa boherejwe mu kigo cya HMP Long Lartin kugira ngo bakemure imvururu.
Abakozi batandatu bavuye mu bitaro bavurwa ibikomere byabo.
Nta bwoko ubwo ari bwo bwose bw'urugomo tuzakomeza kwihanganira mu magereza yacu, kandi abateye imvururu bazahabwa igipolisi, kandi birashoboka ko bazakomeza kumara igihe kirekire cyane muri gereza.
Gereza ya HMP Long Lartin ifite imfungwa zisaga 500, harimo bamwe mu bagizi ba nabi bakomeye muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika.
Muri Kamena, umuyobozi w'iyo gereza yajyanywe mu bitaro kubera ko umwe mu mfungwa yari yaramufashe.
Byongeye kandi, mu kwezi k'Ukwakira umwaka ushize, abapolisi barwanya imvururu, byabaye ngombwa ko bajya muri gereza kugira ngo bahagarike imvururu zikomeye, aho abafashwe bagendaga bagaba ibitero ku bakozi bakoresheje inkoni za billiard.
Inkubi y'umuyaga Rosa yabaye igitero ku mijyi ya Phoenix, Las Vegas na Salt Lake City, aho imyuzure y'ibitotsi (ibice byumye bishobora kungukirwa)
Ni gake cyane kubona umuyaga w'ishuheri muri Arizona, ariko bizashoboka mu cyumweru gitaha, mu gihe inkubi y'umuyaga Rosa izaba imaze kurangiza ingufu zayo, igana ubutayu bwo mu majyepfo ashyira uburengerazuba, aho hari ibyago by'imyuzure itunguranye.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe imibare y'ikirere cyatanze umuburo ku byerekeye imyuzure ishobora kuba kuwa mbere no kuwa gatanu; igihuhusi kizatangira mu burengerazuba bwa Arizona, kijye mu majyepfo no mu burasirazuba bwa Nevada, kizaca muri leta ya California no mu majyepfo ashyira uburasirazuba bwa Utah, kizaca mu mijyi nka Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas na Salt Lake City.
Rosa azajya i Phoenix ku wa Kabiri, ariko imvura nyinshi izagwa ku wa Mbere izamuburira.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe imibare y'ikirere cya Phoenix cyanditse kuri Twitter kiti "Kuva mu mwaka wa 1950, inkubi z'imiyaga icumi zaturutse mu birometero 200 uvuye i Phoenix, zakomeje kuba ibihuha cyangwa ibihuha.
Katrina (1967) yari inkubi y'umuyaga yari ku birometero 40 uvuye ku mupaka wa AZ".
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe iby'inkubi z'umuyaga giteganya ko amazi ashobora kuzamuka agera kuri santimetero ebyiri cyangwa eshanu, ndetse n'amazi ashobora kuzamuka agera kuri santimetero esheshatu mu karere ka Mogollon muri Arizona.
Ku bindi bice byo mu majyepfo ashyira uburengerazuba bw'ubutayu (harimo hagati mu misozi ya Rocky na Great Basin), amazi azakoranwa hagati ya santimetero 1-2; ahantu hiherereye, ashobora gukoranwa santimetero 4.
Ku bantu biteze imyuzure itunguranye, imvura y'amashu ishobora kuba umugisha ku bw'amapfa y'igihe gito igihugu cyahuye na yo.
Ibiza ntibigomba gufatwa uko bitari, ariko iyi mvura y'urujojo ishobora gutuma habaho amapfa mu majyepfo ashyira uburengerazuba.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya amapfa, 40% by'intara ya Arizona iri mu bihe by'amapfa akomeye, akaba ari yo kiciro cya kabiri kiri hejuru, nk'uko byatangajwe n'ikigo cy'amakuru cyitwa weather.com.
Mbere na mbere, inzira y'inkubi y'umuyaga Rosa izanyura mu gice cya Baja California cyo muri Megizike.
Umuyaga wa Rosa uzakomeza kwiyongera ku cyumweru mu gitondo, ugere ku muvuduko wa kilometero 85 mu isaha, mu birometero 385 mu majyepfo ya Punta Eugenia muri Mexique, ugera ku muvuduko wa kilometero 12 mu isaha.
Iyi nkubi y'umuyaga iri gushaka amazi y'igikatu yo mu nyanja ya Pasifika, bituma idakomeza kugira imbaraga.
Biteganyijwe ko izaba igeze muri Mexique ku wa Mbere nyuma ya saa sita cyangwa mu ijoro ry'ejo.
Ibice bimwe na bimwe bya Megizike bishobora guhura n'imiyaga ikaze, bituma haba n'akaga ko habaho imyuzure.
Nk'uko tubikesha urubuga rwa weather.com, "imvura y'isegenya ishobora kugwa ku gipimo cya santimetero 3 kugeza kuri 6 kuva muri Baja California kugera muri Sonora mu majyepfo ashyira uburengerazuba, kandi ishobora kugwaho santimetero 10 mu duce tumwe na tumwe".
Nyuma yaho, Rosa izanyura mu majyaruguru ya Mexique nk'inkubi y'umuyaga y'ishuheri mbere yo kugera ku mupaka wa Arizona nk'icuraburindi ry'ishuheri mu masaha ya saa sita z'ejo kuwa kabiri; nyuma yaho, izanyura muri Arizona, igana mu majyepfo muri Utah ku wa kabiri nijoro.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe inkubi z'imiyaga cyavuze ko "ibihuha bikomeye cyane bishobora gutera imvura y'amahindu y'i Rosa cyangwa ibihuha byayo, ari ibihuha bikomeye cyane bishobora gutera muri Baja California, mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Sonora no mu butayu bwo mu majyepfo ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika".
Iyo mvura izatera imyuzure ikaze n'imyuzure y'ibishingwe mu butayu n'imyuzure mu misozi.
