Abantu babarirwa mu magana bahitanywe n'umutingito na tsunami muri Indoneziya, umubare w'abapfuye ukomeje kwiyongera
Ku wa Gatandatu, abategetsi bavuze ko abantu bagera kuri 384 bapfuye mu mpanuka y'isi n'ibisasu bya tsunami byibasiye ikirwa cya Sulawesi muri Indoneziya, abenshi muri bo bapfuye igihe imiraba ikaze yasenyaga imishike.
Abantu babarirwa mu magana bateraniye mu mujyi wa Palu kuwa gatanu bizihiza ibirori, ariko ku mugoroba inkuba z'imetero esheshatu (18 ft) zashenye inkengero, abantu benshi barapfa, ibintu byose byari mu nzira birasenyuka.
Tsunami yatewe n'umutingito wari ufite ubukana bwa 7.5.
"Imburi ya tsunami yatanzwe ejo, ariko abantu bari bakiri ku nkombe bakora ibikorwa bitandukanye kandi ntibahise bahunga, bituma bahinduka imbata", Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, uhagarariye ikigo cya Indonesia gishinzwe kwirinda ibiza (BNPB) mu kiganiro cyabereye i Jakarta.
" Tsunami yarimbuye imodoka, ibiti n'amazu, irimbura ibintu byose byari mu karere", niko Nugroho avuga.
"Abantu benshi bari mu biti bahunga tsunami, ariko bamwe barokotse", nk'uko uwo mudepite yabitangaje.
Abantu bagera ku 16.700 ni bo bageze mu bigo 24 byo mu mujyi wa Palo.
Amafoto yafashwe n'ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya ibiza, agaragaza amazu n'ubucuruzi byasenyutse, ibiraro byasenyutse n'imisigiti yaguye mu mazi.
Ibikurikiraho by'umutingito byakomeje kugaba igitero ku nkombe z'icyo gihugu ku wa Gatandatu.
Imitingito yibasiye akarere gafite abaturage miliyoni 2.4.
Raporo y'ikigo cya Indonesia gishinzwe gusesengura no gushyira mu bikorwa ikoranabuhanga (BPPT) ivuga ko imbaraga z'umutingito ukomeye wabaye ku wa Gatanu, zikubye incuro 200 iz'igisasu cya kirimbuzi cyatewe i Hiroshima mu ntambara ya kabiri y'isi.
Ikigo cyavuze ko aho uwo mujyi uherereye, uri mu kigobe kirekire kandi cyoroshye, bishobora kuba ari byo byatumye tsunami iba ikomeye.
Mugroho yavuze ko iyi mpanuka yabaye ku kigero cyo hejuru, aho amazu abarirwa mu bihumbi, ibitaro, amaduka n'amahoteli byasenyutse burundu.
Mu nzu z'inyubako zangijwe, havumbuwe imibiri y'abantu benshi, abandi 540 barakomereka, abandi 29 baraburirwa irengero.
Nugroho yavuze ko umubare w'abapfuye ushobora kwiyongera ndetse n'ibiza bishobora kwiyongera mu birometero 300 by'inyanja ya Palu, cyane cyane ahantu hitwa Donggala, hafi y'ikirere.
