Ubugiriki, bwari bufite intara yitwaga Macedonia, iracyemeza ko izina ry'abaturanyi bayo bo mu majyaruguru rifite aho rihuriye n'ubutaka bwayo, bityo bibuza ko bujya muri NATO no mu Bwongereza.
Leta z'ibihugu byombi zageze ku masezerano muri Kamena ashingiye ku izina rishya ryashyizweho, ariko abanzi b'igihugu bavuga ko iryo hinduka ryangiza ubwoko bw'abaturage benshi b'Abaslavya bo muri Macedonia.
Perezida Gjorge Ivanov yatangaje ko atazatora muri iyo referendumu, kandi ko kwamagana ibikorwa byo kwiyamamaza byatumye abantu bibaza niba azabasha kubona 50% by'amajwi akenewe mu matora kugira ngo abe yemewe.
Iki ni ikibazo cyabajijwe ku rupapuro rw'itora: "Mbese mushyigikiye kuba abanyamuryango ba OTAN n'Ubwongereza mu masezerano y'u Bugereki?"
Abashyigikiye iryo hinduka ry'izina, barimo Minisitiri w'Intebe Zoran Zaev, bavuga ko ari byiza ko u Bubiligi buhabwa amahirwe yo kwinjira mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi na NATO, kuko ari kimwe mu bihugu byashinzwe igihe Yugosilaviya yasenyukaga.
Olivera Georgijevska w'imyaka 79 y'amavuko, yavuze ati: "Nje gutora ku hazaza h'igihugu cyacu, ku rubyiruko rwa Macedonia, kugira ngo rushobore kubaho mu bwisanzure, mu gihe cy'ubumwe bw'u Burayi, kuko bizatuma tugira ubuzima bw'umutekano".
Nubwo nta ruhare rufatika rubigiramo, hari abadepite benshi bemeye ko bazashyigikira ibyavuye mu matora kugira ngo bibe byanze bikunze.
Guhindura izina bisaba ko abadepite bagera kuri bitatu bya gatatu by'abadepite bemeza ko ari byo.
Komisiyo y'amatora y'iyo leta yatangaje ko nta makuru y'uko hari ibyago by'imvura yatangajwe mbere ya saa kumi n'imwe z'umugoroba.
Nyamara, 16% by'abemerewe gutora nibo batanze amajwi, ugereranyije na 34% mu matora ya nyuma y'inteko ishinga amategeko yo mu 2016, aho 66% by'abemerewe gutora batanze amajwi.
"Nagiye gutora kubera abana banjye, umwanya wacu uri mu Burayi", niko Gjose Tanevsky, umutagatifu w'imyaka 62 wo mu murwa mukuru Skopje, yavuze.
Minisitiri w'Intebe wa Macedonia, Zoran Zaev, umugore we Zorica n'umwana wabo Dushko, mu matora ya referendumu ya Macedonia, bahisemo guhindura izina ry'igihugu no kwemeza ko igihugu cyabo kizaba umunyamuryango wa NATO n'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, Strumic, muri Macedonia, ku itariki ya 30 Nzeri 2018.
Imbere y'inteko ishinga amategeko mu mujyi wa Skopje, Vladimir Kavardarkov w'imyaka 54 yari arimo ategura ikibuga gito n'urwego rwo kuzamuka imbere y'amaduka y'abashakaga kwamagana amatora.
