Ariko ibyo si byo nshaka mu politiki.
Mu myaka 32 ishize, ubwo nari umunyeshuri, naterwaga inkunga n'uburangare bwa leta ya Thatcher, navuye mu ishuri maze ntangira gukora imirimo ya leta nari nkeneye cyane - nk'umujyanama w'akarere cyangwa minisitiri wa leta.
Sinigeze mpisha imyizerere yanjye ya politiki, si mu nomero ya nyuma.
Nta muntu n'umwe wo mu mujyi wa Nottingham y'iburasirazuba uzongera kwibaza ku myizerere yanjye ya politiki n'amakimbirane mfite n'ubuyobozi buriho.
Icyo nabwira abashyigikiye icyemezo cyo kuwa gatanu ni uko mu gihe igihugu kirimo kigenda kigana muri Brexit izabangamira amazu yacu, ubucuruzi n'ibikorwa bya leta, sinumva impamvu abantu batakaza igihe n'imbaraga mu gushidikanya ku budahemuka bwanjye ku buyobozi bw'ishyaka ry'abakozi.
Ariko ubutumwa bwanjye nyakuri si ubwo gushyigikira Nottingham, ahubwo ni ubwo kubwira intore zanjye, zaba ziri mu ishyaka ry'abakozi cyangwa zitari zo, ko ntewe ishema no kuba nkorera mwebwe, kandi ndabizeza ko nta ngamba zizatuma nkomeza gukora ku nyungu zanyu, nta ngamba z'iterabwoba cyangwa z'amacakubiri ya politiki zizambuza.
Chris Leslie ni umudepite mu Nteko Ishinga Amategeko y'intara ya Nottingham y'iburasirazuba.
