Ni yo mpamvu, mu matora ya Perezida Trump, intego y'ayo materaniro atanu mu cyumweru gitaha ari ugukomeza ibikorwa by'abakorerabushake no gufasha abarepubulikani gukomeza ubwiganze bafite muri Sena no mu Nteko Ishinga Amategeko".
"Iki kibazo cya Congres ni ingenzi cyane, kandi Perezida azagerageza kujya mu bihugu byinshi bishoboka uko azajya mu bikorwa byo kwiyamamaza", ni ko umuvugizi w'ishyaka rya Trump yabwiye Reuters atavuze amazina ye.
Biteganyijwe ko izabera muri Wesbanco Arena i Wheeling, igiterane cy'uyu munsi kizatuma abafana bo muri Ohio na Pennsylvania ndetse n'itangazamakuru ryo mu mujyi wa Pittsburgh, babona amakuru menshi, nk'uko bitangazwa na West Virginia Metro News.
Ku wa Gatandatu, ni ubwa kabiri Trump asuye leta ya Virginia mu kwezi gushize, aho yatsindiye amatora mu 2016 ku majwi 40 ku ijana.
Trump mu by'ukuri arashaka gufasha Senateri Patrick Morrisey wo mu ishyaka ry'aba Repubulika muri Virginia, ari na we akurikiye.
Ntabwo ari ikimenyetso cyiza kuri Morrissey ko perezida agomba kujya muri Amerika gufasha mu bikorwa byo kwiyamamaza.
Ryder Cup 2018: Amakipe ya Amerika azakomeza mu mikino y'umunsi w'icyumweru
Nyuma y'ibihe bitatu by'umukino umwe, byari bikwiriye ko umukino w'umunsi wa gatandatu w'umunsi wa kane uba ari wo mukino Ryder Cup yari ikeneye.
Ikibazo cy'ingenzi ni uko ari igishushanyo mbonera cy'umukino, abakinnyi bemera, ariko nta kindi.
None se ni ikihe gihe cyiza cyo kubikora?
Jordan Spieth yagize ati "bari bafite amanota atandatu y'imbere, ubu bafite ane, bityo ndatekereza ko ubu ari igihe cyo kugira icyo bakora".
Birumvikana ko u Burayi bufite amanota ane ku 12 ariho.
Abanyamerika, nkuko Spieth abivuga, bumva ko umuyaga utagenda neza, kandi bakeneye ubufasha, cyane cyane Spieth na Justin Thomas, bakinnye hamwe maze batsinda amanota atatu kuri ane.
Spieth yari afite imbaraga nyinshi, kuva ku mukino w'ubusa kugeza ku mukino w'amabara, kandi arimo ayobora mu buryo bw'intangarugero.
Uko imikino yagendaga irushaho gukomera, ni na ko yakomeje kuririmba cyane, maze atsinda igitego gikomeye, atsinda ibitego bine, nyuma y'uko Thomas atsinzwe ibitego bibiri bikurikirana.
Yishimiye undi muriri umeze nk'uwo yatsindiye mu mukino wa 15, byerekana ko ikipe y'Amerika itarasiwe mu irushanwa.
Spieth yaravuze ati "ugomba kwihangana kandi ukita ku mukino wawe gusa".
Ni byo abo bakinnyi ba ruhago basigaye bafite.
Dufite imyobo 18 yo gukora.
Abakinnyi bonyine batsinze Spieth na Thomas mu minsi ibiri ishize ni Francesco Molinari na Tommy Fleetwood, bombi babaye abakinnyi bakomeye mu mateka y'igikombe cya Ryder.
Abo bashakanye b'i Burayi badasanzwe ariko bafite ubwiza, ku bantu bane, bane ni bo bahakana ko batazabishobora.
Hollywood ni yo yari itsinda rimwe rukumbi ritari ryajugunyaga imishino ku wa Gatandatu nyuma ya saa sita, ariko ku wa Gatandatu mu gitondo, ku wa Gatanu nyuma ya saa sita, kandi ku wa Gatanu, bari barangije icyenda.
Uyu mukino hamwe n'imbaraga z'abantu benshi bari baje kuri uwo mukino, byatumye uwo mukino uba umukino ukomeye ku cyumweru. Nta mukinnyi w'umunyaburayi ukomeye kurusha Fleetwood na Molinari, washoboraga gufunga intsinzi y'u Burayi ku munsi w'izuba rya Le Golf National.
Ni byiza ko aba bombi baba ahantu hatandukanye.
Ariko kandi, kuvuga iby'Abanyaburayi bakomeye biracyari kare cyane.
Bubba Watson na Webb Simpson bongeye gukora cyane kuri Sergio Garcia, umukinnyi wa mbere mu itsinda rya kane, aho yari ahanganye na Alex Noen.
Bashyize imbunda n'ibikoresho bibiri imbere y'umunya Espagne n'Umusuwisi ku mwobo utarigeze wegera cyane.
Ariko ku cyumweru, nta muntu wari ukiriho wo kugufasha.
Aba bane bari bashishikajwe no kureba hafi uburyo abashakanye bakorana, inama batangaga, n'izo batatangaga, no kubona uko umuntu ashobora guhindura ingamba mu kanya gato.
Uburayi bwagize ikipe nziza, kandi bwari bufite amahirwe menshi yo kugera ku mukino wa nyuma, ariko umukino w'abakinnyi bane wagaragaje ko ikipe ya Amerika ifite imbaraga zo kurwana, nubwo hari bamwe, cyane cyane Stateside, bibazaga.
U Burayi bufite imbere 10-6 mu mukino wa nyuma wa Ryder Cup
U Burayi bwabonye amahirwe menshi mu mukino wa nyuma wa Ryder Cup nyuma y'uko ku wa Gatandatu itsinda ry'abakinnyi bane ryabonye amanota 10-6 ku ikipe y'igihugu cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
Aba bombi bahumekewe Tommy Fleetwood na Francesco Molinari batsinze inshuro ebyiri Tiger Woods wari washyizeho imihati myinshi, maze bagera ku manota ane y'agaciro kugeza ubu muri Le Golf Nationale.
Thomas Bjorn wo mu Burayi, wari ugiye gushaka igikombe cya Hazelin yari amaze imyaka ibiri atakaje, yabaye umuyobozi muri iki gitondo, atsinda umukino 3-1.
Amerika yarwanye cyane, itsinda imikino ibiri, ariko ntiyashoboye gutsinda.
Bakeneye amanota umunani ya Jim Fury mu mikino 12 y'umunsi w'icyumweru kugira ngo bakomeze kuba abambere.
Fleetwood ni we musore mushya umwe rukumbi w'umunyamerika watsinze amanota ane yikurikiranya kandi hamwe na Molinieri, bakunze kwitwa "Molliwood" nyuma y'impera z'icyumweru nziza, ni uwa kabiri mu mateka y'irushanwa rya Ryder Cup batsinze amanota ane mu mikino ine.
Nyuma yo gutsinda Woods na Patrick Reed mu mikino ine, yatsinze umukino neza cyane batsinda Woods wari unaniwe na Bryson Dechambeau, umukinnyi mushya wa Amerika, ibitego 5-4.
Woods, nyuma yo gukina imikino ibiri ku wa Gatandatu, yagaragaje ko yari afite imbaraga, ariko yatsinzwe imikino 19 muri 29 yakinnye mu mikino ine y'amabara atandatu n'amabara ane, imikino 7 ikurikirana.
Justin Rose yafashe ikiruhuko cyo gukina umupira wa Fourball mu gitondo agaruka mu kibuga ari kumwe na Henrik Stenson batsinda Dustin Johnson na Brooks Koepka 2 na 1 mu mikino ine.
U Burayi ntibwigeze bubona inzira mu minsi myiza kandi itoshye y'amajyepfo y'uburengerazuba bwa Paris.
Abatsinze inshuro eshatu, Jordan Spiethe na Justin Thomas, bashyizeho amanota abiri ku wa gatandatu.
Batsinze 2-1 batsinze umukinnyi w'umunya Espagne Jon Rahm na Ian Poulter muri fourballs hanyuma banatsinda Poulter na Rory McIlroy nyuma yo kubura ibibanza bibiri bya mbere muri 4&3 Fours.
Ni inshuro ebyiri gusa mu mateka y'irushanwa rya Ryder Cup ikipe yashoboye kurenga itandukaniro ry'amanota ane ikinjira mu mikino y'abantu ku giti cyabo, nubwo uruhande rwa Fury rwakeneye gusa guhuza kugirango rukomeze igihembo.
Iyo umaze kuba uwa kabiri mu minsi ibiri, nyuma y'uko ufashe umwanya wa mbere ku cyumweru, uba uri imbere ye.
Koreya ya Ruguru yanze guhagarika intwaro nta cyizere na gito itanga.
Minisitiri w'ububanyi n'amahanga wa Koreya ya Ruguru yabwiye Umuryango w'Abibumbye kuwa gatandatu ko ibihano by'Amerika bikomeje gutuma abantu batakariza icyizere Amerika, kandi ko nta buryo na bumwe Koreya ya Ruguru izahagarika gushaka intwaro za kirimbuzi.
Ri Yong Ho yabwiye inama rusange y'uyu muryango ko Koreya ya Ruguru yafashe ingamba zikomeye umwaka ushize, zirimo guhagarika igerageza ry'intwaro za kirimbuzi n'ibisasu bya misile, guhagarika ahantu hakorerwa igerageza ry'intwaro za kirimbuzi no kwemeza ko izahagarika iterambere ry'ikoranabuhanga n'intwaro za kirimbuzi.
Yagize ati "Nyamara, ntituzi igisubizo gihagije kizatangwa na Amerika".
"Aho Amerika itazitabira nta cyizere kizaba kiriho ku mutekano w'igihugu cyacu, kandi nta na rimwe dushobora kureka intwaro zacu ubwa mbere".
Rik yasubiyemo ibirego bisanzwe bya Koreya ya Ruguru ku kwamagana Washington mu rwego rwa gahunda yo kugabanya intwaro kirimbuzi mu byiciro  aho Koreya ya Ruguru yari guhembwa kubera gutera intambwe buhoro buhoro.
Rik Kim Jong Un na Donald Trump bavuga ku nama ya mbere ya Perezida wa Amerika n'umuyobozi wa Koreya ya Ruguru yabereye i Singapore ku ya 12 Kamena ubwo Kim yiyemezaga "kugabanya intwaro kirimbuzi ku mugabane wa Koreya", naho Trump yiyemezaga gutanga umutekano wa Koreya ya Ruguru.
Koreya ya Ruguru ikomeje gushaka uburyo bwo kurangiza intambara yo muri Koreya yo mu 1950-1953, ariko Amerika ivuga ko Pyongyang ari yo yabanza gushyira intwaro hasi.
Washington yanze kumva amajwi mpuzamahanga asaba ko ibihano byafatiwe Koreya ya Ruguru bigabanywa.
Rik yagize ati "Amerika yongeye kuvuga ko bagomba gushyira intwaro hasi mbere, kandi ikomeza kongera igipimo cy'ibihano kugira ngo ibashishikarize kugera ku ntego yabo, kandi irwanya itangazo ryo kurangiza intambara".
"Igitekerezo cy'uko ibiboko bishobora gutuma twumvira amategeko ni igitekerezo kidashyize mu gaciro ku batatwisanze.
Ikibazo ni uko guhora bihana bituma abantu batongera kwizerana".
Ariko Rick ntiyavuze ku nama ya kabiri ya Kim na Trump yari yatangajwe n'umuyobozi wa Amerika mu Nteko Ishinga Amategeko mu ntangiriro z'iki cyumweru.
Minisitiri w'intebe w'u Buyapani yavuze ko mu mezi atanu ashize, Kim Jong-un yahuye inshuro eshatu n'umuyobozi wa Koreya y'Epfo, Moon Jae-in, yongeraho ko iyo Koreya y'Epfo iza kuba ari yo yivuguruza aho kuba Amerika, ibikorwa byo guca intwaro kirimbuzi mu gihugu cya Koreya y'Epfo ntibyari kuba byarahagaritswe.
Ariko, ijwi rya Ri ryari ritandukanye cyane n'iry'ijambo rye mu mwaka ushize, aho yabwiye Inteko Rusange ya Loni ko Koreya ya Ruguru yari igomba gushyira ibisasu byayo kuri Amerika, nyuma y'aho Perezida Trump "Perezida Satani" Kim "Mr Missile" amwise "Inteko y'ubwicanyi".
Muri uyu mwaka, mu muryango w'abibumbye, Trump, wavuze ko azasenya Koreya ya ruguru, yashimiye Kim kubera ubutwari bwe bwo gutera intambwe yo gushyira intwaro hasi, ariko avuga ko hakiri byinshi byo gukora kandi ko ibihano bizakomeza kugeza Koreya ya ruguru ivuyeho intwaro za kirimbuzi.
Ku wa Gatatu, Trump yavuze ko nta gihe afite cyo kubikora, yaba mu myaka ibiri, mu myaka itatu cyangwa mu mezi atanu ari imbere - nta cyo bitwaye".
Ubushinwa n'Uburusiya bumva ko Inama y'Umutekano y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ikwiriye guha agaciro Pyongyang kubera ubudahemuka bwayo.
Ariko umunyamabanga wa Leta zunze ubumwe z'Amerika, Mike Pompeo, yabwiye akanama k'umutekano ka Loni kuwa kane, ati "Ibihano by'akanama k'umutekano bigomba gukomeza gushyirwa mu bikorwa, nta kabuza, kugeza igihe tuzamenya neza ko ibikorwa byo kugabanya intwaro za kirimbuzi ari ukuri".
Inama y'Umutekano y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye yemeje ku bw'umwihariko ibihano byafatiwe Koreya ya Ruguru kuva mu 2006 mu rwego rwo gukumira inkunga ya Pyongyang mu bikorwa byayo bya kirimbuzi n'iby'ubumara.
Pompeo yahuye na Ri hanze y'inama y'inteko rusange ya ONU, hanyuma avuga ko azongera kujya i Pyongyang gutegura inama y'umushyikirano ya kabiri.
Pompeo yakoze ingendo eshatu muri Koreya ya Ruguru muri uyu mwaka, ariko ubwa nyuma ntibyamuhiriye.
Ubwo yagarukaga i Pyongyang muri Nyakanga, avuga ko hari ikintu kimwe gusa cyagezweho kuri Koreya ya Ruguru, nyuma y'amasaha menshi y'ibinyoma avuga ko ibyo yasabaga byari nk'iby'abanyarugomo".
Koreya ya Ruguru yari yarahiriye mu nama yahuje Moon ko izatanga aho ikorera za misile n'aho ikorera ibitwaro kirimbuzi mu gihe Amerika izaba yemeye gufata ingamba.
Yabwiye Kim ko "ingamba z'umutekano" yari arimo gushaka harimo n'iz'umutekano Trump yari yemeye ko Singapore izatanga, kandi avuga ku byo gukora mu rwego rwo kuvugurura umubano na Washington.
Abanyeshuri bo muri kaminuza ya Harvard bakoze amasomo yo kuruhuka bihagije.
Ishuri rya Harvard muri uyu mwaka rizahatira abanyeshuri barangije amashuri yisumbuye kuryama cyane, mu rwego rwo kurwanya umuco w'uburezi ugenda wiyongera, wo kunywa ikawa mu ijoro.
Umwarimu umwe yabonye ko muri kaminuza nziza ku isi, abanyeshuri birengagiza igihembo cy'ingenzi mu kwita ku buzima bwabo.
Charles Czeisler, umwarimu wigisha ubuvuzi bw'ibitotsi mu ishuri ry'ubuvuzi rya Harvard akaba n'impuguke mu bitaro bya Brigham na Women, yateguye amasomo atekereza ko ari aya mbere muri iki gihugu.
Yatangiye kwiga ubwo yatangaga ikiganiro ku ngaruka zo kubura ibitotsi mu gihe yari akiri umunyeshuri.
"Umukobwa umwe yaje ansanga ku musozo arambaza ati 'kuki ngomba kubikora ubu, ndi jyenyine mu mwaka wanjye wa nyuma w'ishuri?'
Yambwiye ko nta muntu n'umwe wigeze amubwira akamaro ko gusinzira neza, ibyo bikaba byaranantunguye.
Iyi nyigisho, yatangijwe bwa mbere muri uyu mwaka, yereka abanyeshuri ingaruka zo gusinzira neza ku masomo no ku mikino ngororamubiri, ndetse no kuzamura imibereho yabo.
Paul Barreira, umwarimu wigisha iby'indwara zo mu mutwe ku ishuri ry'ubuvuzi rya Harvard akaba n'umuyobozi w'ibigo nderabuzima muri kaminuza, yavuze ko kaminuza yafashe icyemezo cyo gutangiza iyi nyigisho nyuma yo kubona ko abanyeshuri bayo baryamaga igihe gito mu cyumweru.
Iyi gahunda y'amasaha menshi, ikubiyemo ibice bitandukanye binyuranye.
Igice kimwe kigaragaza icyumba abanyeshuri bafatiramo amacupa ya kawa, ibitambaro, abakinnyi n'ibitabo kugira ngo barebe ingaruka za kafeyine n'urumuri, n'ingaruka zo kuryama nabi bigira ku mikino ngororangingo n'akamaro ko kuryama neza.
Mu kindi gice, babwiraga abitabiriye iki cyigisho ko kubura ibitotsi bishobora gutuma barwara indwara y'umutima, indwara yo kwiheba cyangwa kanseri.
Ikarita ya campus ikoresha amashusho y'ikoranabuhanga, isaba abitabiriye gutekereza ku ngeso zabo za buri munsi.
"Turabizi ko tudashobora guhindura imyifatire y'abanyeshuri mu ijoro rimwe.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, abantu benshi barangiza bakamara igihe runaka barya ibyokurya by'umubiri, bakanywa inzoga, cyangwa bakanywa inzoga z'amavuta.
Avuga ko hari umuco w'ubwibone mu gukora naupasa, kandi ko ikoranabuhanga rigezweho n'igitutu cy'abanyeshuri kigenda cyiyongera bituma ikibazo cyo gukora naupasa gito cyane kirushaho kwiyongera.
Ati "Gusinzira neza, hamwe no gusinzira neza, bigomba kuba intwaro y'ibanga yo kurwanya imihangayiko, umunaniro n'imihangayiko, ariko no kongera ibiro, kuko gusinzira bihagije bituma ubwonko bwumva bwarashonje, kandi ni ko tuzajya tubikora igihe cyose".
Raymond So, umunyakalifoniya w'imyaka 19 wiga ibijyanye n'ibinyabuzima n'ibinyabuzima yafashije Porofeseri Czeisler gukora iyi nyigisho, kandi yari mu masomo ye ya mbere mu mwaka wa mbere muri Harvard.
Yavuze ko iyo myitozo yamuhumuye amaso ndetse imutera inkunga yo kwitabira amasomo yari agize igice cy'isomero.
Icyizere afite ni uko intambwe ikurikiraho ari ugusaba abanyeshuri barangije amasomo yabo gukora ubushakashatsi bufite aho buhuriye na bwo, mbere yo kujya mu kigo bahanganye na cyo.
Prof Czeisler arasaba abanyeshuri gushyiraho indangururamajwi kugirango bamenye igihe cyo kuryama, ndetse no gukanguka, kandi bamenye ingaruka mbi z'urumuri rw'ubururu rucyekwa n'amashusho ya elegitoronike n'amatara ya LED, bishobora guhindura imiterere ya circadienne, kandi bigatera ibibazo byo gusinzira.
Mengaka yatsinze ingabo za Gerrard
Ranger zongeye gutsindwa ubwo Dolly Menga yabaga ari ku ruhande rwa Steven Gerrard 1-0 i Livingston.
Bari bategereje gutsinda ku nshuro ya mbere nyuma yo gutsinda 4-1 muri St. Johnstone muri Gashyantare, ariko ikipe ya Gary Holt yateje itsindwa rya kabiri ry'ikipe ya Gerrard mu mukino we wa 18 nk'umutoza, amanota ye umunani atuma Hearts yo mu bakuru ba Landbrokes Championship ihunga.
Menga yakoze igitego iminota irindwi mbere y'igihe cyo kwishyura, maze umusaruro w'abakinnyi ba Ranger utuma hatabaho guhuza.
Abakinnyi ba Rangers ubu bari ku mwanya wa gatandatu, ariko Livingston yazamutse ku mwanya wa gatatu, aho bari inyuma ya Hibernian ku gitego kimwe gusa.
Ikibazo cyashoboraga kuba gikomeye cyane kuruta icyo mu gihe aba Ranger bari bakeneye Calum Spence wari ufite amaguru y'amababa, ku bw'igikomere cyo mu mutwe, bivugwa ko yishwe n'ikintu cyatewe giturutse hanze.
Gerrard yahindutse inshuro umunani, bituma Ayr igera mu mikino ya 1⁄2 y'igikombe cya Betfred.
Ku rundi ruhande, Holt yari afite Livi 11, watwaye Heartse igitego kimwe mu cyumweru gishize, kandi yari kwishimira ko imyenda ye y'amabara meza yatumaga abanzi be bahunga buri tsinda.
Abakinnyi ba Rangers bari bafite igikombe, ariko Livingston ni we wabonye inyungu nyinshi mu mikino yabo.
Igitego cya Scott Pittman ku ruhande rwa Mengwa cya Allan McGregor cyari kigomba kuba cyarinjiye mu kibuga ariko umukinnyi wo hagati ntiyabashaga kugikoresha.
Igitego cy'umunyempano cya Keaghan Jacobs cyabonye kapiteni Craig Halkett, ariko mugenzi we Alan Lithgow yashoboye kumurenga gusa mu gice cy'inyuma.
Abakinnyi ba Rangers bari bafite ububasha, ariko mu gice cya nyuma cy'umukino, byasaga n'aho icyizere cyabo cyari cyinshi kurusha uko bari babyiteze.
Alfredo Morelos yumvaga ko agomba kuba yaratsinze penaliti ku mpera za kimwe cya kane ubwo yagiranaga ikibazo na Steven Lawless, ariko umucamanza Steven Thomson yanze kumva ubujurire bw'uwo mukoloni.
Yatsinze ibitego bibiri gusa bya Rangers mu gice cya mbere, ariko Liam Kelly wahoze ari rutahizamu wa Ibrox nta kibazo yagize kubera igitego cya Lassana Coulibaly n'igitego cyoroheje cya Ovie Ejaria.
Igitego cya mbere cya Livi ku munota wa 34 gishobora kuba cyaragize ingaruka mbi ku mukino ariko nta muntu wahakana ko byari bifite akamaro, cyane cyane iyo urebye imihati ikomeye bashyizeho.
N'ubu, abakinnyi ba Rangers bananiwe guhangana n'umukino wa Jacobs wari warangiye.
Scott Arfield ntiyagize icyo akora ubwo Declan Gallagher yahaga umupira Scott Robinson, maze ahitamo ku bwisanzure Menga mu mukino wo guhagarika.
Gerrard yagize icyo akora mu kiruhuko asimbuza Coulibaly Ryan Kent, kandi ihinduka ryahise rigira ingaruka ubwo umurenge wa Morelos wahabwaga umurongo, ariko Kelly ukomeye yiruka hanze yumurongo we kugira ngo awubuze.
Ariko Livingston yakomeje guhatira abakinnyi bo hanze gukina umukino bakundaga, Lithgow na Halkett bakinaga igihe kirekire nyuma yo gutanga byinshi.
Ikipe ya Holt yari ifite amahirwe yo kongera imbere, ariko McGregor yihanganye cyane mbere yo gutera imbere avuye mu ihembe rya Lithgow.
Glenn Middleton wasimbuye Rangers yongeye gusaba penaliti ubwo yari yahagaze kuri Jacobs, ariko Thomson yongeye kumwirengagiza.
Almanac: Umushakashatsi wa Geiger
Noneho, ku ipaji yo mu gitabo cyacu cyitwa "Dimanche matin": tariki ya 30 Nzeri 1882, imyaka 136 mbere y'uko igihe cyagenwe kigera, umuhanga mu bya fiziki witwaga Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger yavukiye mu Budage.
Geiger yatangije uburyo bwo gutahura no gupima imirasire: kuva mu bushakashatsi bwe, byiswe konti ya Geiger.
Kuva icyo gihe, ni yo yabaye inkomoko ya siyansi, kandi yabaye inkomoko ya pop culture, nko muri filime yo mu 1950 yitwa "Bells of Coronado" yari ifite abakobwa b'abarozi Roy Rogers na Dale Evans bataragiraga ishusho yo kuba abahanga:
Umugabo aramubaza ati "Ibyo ni ibiki?"
Rogers: "Ni imbonerahamwe ya Geiger ikoreshwa mu gushaka ubutare bw'imirasire y'amashanyarazi, nka uranium.
Iyo wambaye ibyo byuma, ushobora kumva ingaruka z'ama atome mu bimera".
Evans: "Yego, turabyumva ubu!"
"Hans" Geiger yapfuye mu mwaka wa 1945, hasigaye iminsi mike ngo yuzuze imyaka 63.
Ariko kandi, ibyo yahimbye byitiriwe izina rye biracyariho.
Urukingo rushya rwa kanseri rushobora kwigisha ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri kubona ingirabuzimafatizo mbi
Urukingo rushya rwa kanseri rushobora kwigisha ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri kubona ingirabuzimafatizo mbi no kuzica.
Urukingo rutuma ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri bwamenya ingirabuzimafatizo zanduye nk'igice cy'umuti.
Ni ugufata ingirabuzimafatizo z'umubiri z'abarwayi, ukazihindura mu byumba by'ubushakashatsi.
Hanyuma bashobora kureba poroteyine ikunda kugaragara mu ndwara nyinshi, hanyuma bakayisubiramo.
Uru rukingo ruri kugeragezwa rurimo gukora neza cyane ku barwayi bafite ubwoko butandukanye bwa kanseri.
Hari umugore wahawe urukingo rutuma umubiri we umenya ingirabuzimafatizo zanduye, bamukiza kanseri y'inkondo y'umura mu gihe cy'amezi arenga 18.
Ibyo ni byo: gufata ingirabuzimafatizo z'umubiri z'umurwayi, ukazihindura mu byumba by'ubushakashatsi kugira ngo "urebe" poroteyine izwiho mu ndwara nyinshi yitwa HER2, hanyuma ukazisubiza muri utwo duce.
