U Bushinwa buvuga ko hari ukwiyongera kwa 14% kw'abanduye SIDA
U Bushinwa bwavuze ko umubare w'abaturage bafite virusi itera SIDA wiyongereyeho 14%.
Abategetsi b'igihugu bashinzwe ubuzima bavuga ko abantu barenga 820,000 bamaze kwandura.
Abantu barenga 40.000 barwaye iki cyorezo mu gihembwe cya kabiri cya 2018 cyonyine.
Abenshi mu barwayi bashya ni abanduye mu mibonano mpuzabitsina, ibyo bikaba ari uguhindura amateka.
Mu buryo bwa gakondo, virusi itera SIDA yakwirakwizwaga mu buryo bwihuse mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'u Bushinwa binyuze mu guterwa amaraso yanduye.
Ariko iyi gahunda yagabanyije umubare w'abantu banduye virusi itera SIDA ku buryo nta n'umwe wari uyirwaye, nk'uko abayobozi b'ubuzima bw'u Bushinwa babivuze mu nama yabereye mu ntara ya Yunnan.
Nyamara buri mwaka, umubare w'abantu bafite virusi itera SIDA n'agakoko gatera SIDA mu Bushinwa wiyongeraho abantu 100,000.
Kwanduzanya SIDA mu mibonano mpuzabitsina ni ikibazo gikomeye mu muryango wa LGBTI mu Bushinwa.
Ubusambanyi bwaraciwe mu Bushinwa mu 1997, ariko ivangura rikorerwa abantu ba LGTB riracyakwirakwira.
Kubera indangagaciro z'iki gihugu, ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko 70%-90% by'abagabo baryamana n'abagabo, amaherezo bashyingiranwa n'umugore.
Impamvu nyinshi zitera indwara zikwirakwira ni uko abantu bakoresha uburyo bwo kurinda mu mibonano mpuzabitsina.
Kuva mu 2003, leta y'Ubushinwa yemeje ko abantu bose bahabwa imiti irebana na virusi itera SIDA mu rwego rwo kurwanya iki kibazo.
Maxine Waters yahakanye amakuru y'abasenateri b'aba republicain yatangajwe n'abakozi be, ahindura "ibinyoma biteje akaga" n'"inyigisho z'ibinyoma"
