Abademokarate bo muri Los Angeles bavuze ko ibyo birego byatewe inkunga n'abahanga n'imbuga za interineti "b'iburyo bw'agahomamunwa".
Waters yagize ati "ibinyoma, ibinyoma n'ibindi binyoma by'akahebwe".
Amakuru yashyizwe ahagaragara mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga yari akubiyemo amakuru y'abasenateri batatu ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Lindsey Graham wo muri Carolina y'Epfo na Mike Lee na Orrin Hatch, bombi bo muri Utah.
Amakuru y'uko hari umuntu utaramenyekana washyize kuri interineti ku wa Kabiri w'iki cyumweru, yashyizwe kuri Capitol Hill mu nama ya Komite ya Sena mu rubanza rw'ibirego by'imyitwarire mibi ku mukandida w'urukiko rw'ikirenga, Brett Kavanaugh.
Ibyo byatangajwe nyuma gato y'aho abasenateri batatu b'Abanyamerika babajije Kavanaugh ibibazo.
Hill yavuze ko imbuga za interineti z'abazunguzayi nka Gateway Pundit na RedState zatangaje ko aderesi ya IP igaragaza isoko yari ifitanye isano n'ibiro bya Waters kandi ko hari umwe mu bakozi ba Waters wasohoye amakuru.
Waters yakomeje agira ati "ibyo birego bidafite ishingiro ni ibinyoma byambaye ubusa kandi ni ibinyoma byambaye ubusa.
"Abakozi banjye - abo imyirondoro yabo, amakuru yabo bwite n'umutekano wabo byashyizwe mu kaga n'ibi birego by'ibinyoma by'uburiganya - nta ruhare na rumwe babigizemo ku bijyanye n'uko ayo makuru yasakaye.
Ibyo birego nta shingiro bifite ni ibinyoma byambaye ubusa".
