Johnny English Strikes Again - isesengura ry'umusare w'umunyagitugu witwa Rowan Atkinson
Ubu ni umuco gushaka ibisobanuro bya Brexit muri filime nshya yose ifite umwihariko w'Abongereza, kandi biragaragara ko ibyo bidakoreshwa muri franchise ya comedy ya action ya Johnny English. Yatangiye mu 2003 na Johnny English maze agaruka mu 2011 na Johnny English Reborn.
Ese kwikinisha ku nkuru igaragaza neza ko turi imyanda, bizatuma igihugu cyacu kigira ubundi buryo bwo kohereza ibicuruzwa?
Uko byagenda kose, Johnny English udafite ubushobozi ufite amaso manini n'amaso y'ibumba, yongeye guhabwa uruhushya rwo gusebanya ku nshuro ya kabiri. Izina rye rigaragaza ko ari igishushanyo cy'urwenya kidasanzwe, cyateguwe mu bihugu bitareba ururimi rw'Icyongereza.
Nubwo afite inyota idasanzwe yo gushimisha, ni umukozi w'ibanga w'umusazi ufite ishusho ya Clouseau, ariko nanone afite ishusho ya Mr Bean n'igice cy'umusore ufasha Chariots of Fire ku birori byo gutangiza imikino Olempike y'i Londres 2012.
Mu matangazo ya televiziyo ya Barclaycard yaribagiwe, uyu mugabo w'umunyamahanga w'amayobera, wakinwaga na Atkinson, ni we mu by'ukuri yatumye habaho akajagari.
Hari ibintu byiza byabaye muri uru rugendo rwa nyuma rwa JE.
Nashimishijwe cyane n'uburyo Johnny English yegereye iyo kajugujugu yambaye intwaro zo mu kinyejana cya hagati, aho imfuruka z'imashini z'umwirongi zakomangaga ku mutwe.
Impano ya Atkinson yo gusetsa iragaragara kumurongo, ariko gusetsa kubura imbaraga kandi birenze urugero, cyane cyane mugihe na firime z'ibimenyetso nka 007 na Mission Impossible ubu zinyura muri comedy mubikoresho byazo.
Iyo myumvire y'urwenya isa n'aho igenewe abana kurusha abantu bakuru, kandi kuri jye, ibikorwa by'ubusazi bya Johnny English si byiza cyangwa se si byiza nk'ubusazi bw'umuntu witwa Bean mu mafilimi ya Atkinson adafite ijwi.
Ubu igitekerezo cy'ingenzi ni uko Ubwongereza bufite ikibazo gikomeye.
Umunyabyaha yinjiye mu muyoboro wa internet wihishe cyane w'abakorera iperereza mu Bwongereza, agaragaza amazina y'abakozi bose b'Abongereza bakora, bituma umukozi w'ibiro by'iperereza w'umunyabyaha arakara, kandi ni uruhare ruto kuri Kevin Eldon.
Ibi ni byinshi cyane kuri Minisitiri w'Intebe ufite imiterere y'ubwibone kandi ikurikiranwa cyane, kuko ubu yataye agaciro muri politiki: Emma Thompson asa neza cyane mu buryo busa na Teresa May, ariko inyandiko ntifasha cyane.
Abajyanama be mu by'ubutasi bamubwiye ko umutungo we wose w'ubutasi uri mu kaga, bityo akaba agomba gushaka umuntu uri mu kiruhuko cy'izabukuru.
Ibyo bisobanura ko Johnny English we ubwe agomba gukora uko ashoboye kose, ubu ni umwarimu mu nzu nziza, ariko yigisha amasomo y'ibanga ku byo gukora nk'umunyamabanga, harimo n'amashyengo meza, kubera ko English atanga ishuri ry'ubutasi mu buryo bwa Rock School.
English yasubijwe i Whitehall mu nama y'ubuvugizi yihutirwa, aho yongeye guhura na mugenzi we wa mbere Bough, wongeye gukinishwa na Ben Miller.
Bough ubu ni umugabo washatse, afitanye umubano n'umuyobozi w'inyubako y'ubwato bw'intambara, Vicki Pepperdine we ntiyakundaga uwo mwanya w'umukire.
Noneho rero, dufite Batman na Robin bongeye gukora ibintu bibi mu Murimo W'ibanga w'Umusumbabyose, bahura n'umugore mwiza cyane wa Olga Kurylenko, Ophelia Bulletova.
Hagati aho, Minisitiri w'Intebe afite amatsiko menshi y'umunya-miliyari w'umuhanga mu ikoranabuhanga uvuga ko ashobora gukemura ibibazo by'ikoranabuhanga mu Bwongereza, akaba ari we munya-miliyari mubi Jason Volta, wakinishijwe na Jake Lacy.
English na Bough batangira urugendo rwabo rw'ubusabusa bambaye nk'abakozi batanga amatike, batwika resitora y'abafaransa, batangira akajagari binyuze mu kwihisha mu bwato bwa Volta, maze English atangira kurakara ubwo yageragezaga gukoresha udupfukamunwa twabo two mu by'ukuri kugira ngo arebe uko inzu ya Volta isa.
Ibice byose by'igitaramo biba bigamije kureba uyu mukino wa nyuma, ariko nubwo ari mwiza kandi ufite urusaku, byose bisa n'ibiri kuri televiziyo y'abana.
Ni ibintu bidasanzwe.
Kandi nk'uko byagenze mu mafilimi menshi ya Johnny English, natangiye kwibaza niba inganda z'ibyamamare z'Abongereza zidashobora guha Rowan Atkinson uruhare rukwiriye impano ye?
Ishyaka ry'abakozi rirahakana ko ryatangiye gukora gahunda yo guha Abongereza iminsi ine y'akazi mu cyumweru, bakishyurwa iminsi itanu.
Ishyaka ry'abakozi rya Jeremy Corbyn riri kwiga ku mugambi wo guhindura ingengabitekerezo, aho Abongereza bakora umunsi umwe mu cyumweru ariko bakishyurwa iminsi itanu.
Biragaragara ko abayobozi b'ibigo by'ubucuruzi bifuza ko amafaranga y'ubwitonzi bw'ubuhanga bwa kirimbuzi, agenerwa abakozi babo, bagatanga umunsi umwe w'ikiruhuko.
