Umunsi mukuru w'umuturage ku isi ni iki, kandi se hari icyo wakoze mu kurwanya ubukene?
Kuri uyu wa gatandatu, i New York hari ibirori by'umuzika ngarukamwaka bita Global Citizen Festival, ibirori by'umuzika ngarukamwaka bihuriza hamwe abahanzi bakomeye bafite intego imwe gusa: gukuraho ubukene ku isi.
Kuri iyi nshuro ya cumi n'indwi, Global Citizen's Festival izazana abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi ku kibuga kinini cya Central Park, atari gusa kwishimira ibitaramo bya Janet Jackson, Cardi B na Shawn Mendes, ahubwo no kongera ubumenyi ku ntego nyayo y'iki gikorwa, ari yo gukuraho ubukene bukabije mbere ya 2030.
Umunsi mukuru w'umuturage ku isi, washinzwe mu 2012, ni ukuramba kw'umushinga w'ubukene ku isi, umushinga w'itsinda mpuzamahanga ry'ubuvugizi ryiteze kurandura ubukene binyuze mu kongera umubare w'abantu barwanya ubukene.
Kugira ngo ubone kwinjira kubuntu kumurika (uretse niba witeguye kwishyura itike ya VIP), abashaka kujya mu gitaramo bagomba gukora imirimo itandukanye cyangwa "ibikorwa", nko kohereza ubutumwa bwa e-imeri, guhamagara umuyobozi w'isi, cyangwa guhamagara mu bundi buryo bwingirakamaro kugirango bafashe kuzamura ubumenyi ku ntego yo kurandura ubukene.
Ariko se Global Citizen yagize icyo igeraho mu rugero rungana iki mu gihe hasigaye imyaka 12 ngo igere ku ntego yayo?
Gushishikariza abantu kugira icyo bakora binyuze mu gukora igitaramo cy'ubuntu, ni igitekerezo gishya, cyangwa ni ikindi cyitwa "clicktivism", ni ukuvuga kugerageza gutuma abantu bumva ko barimo batanga umusaruro binyuze mu gushyira umukono ku nyandiko yo gusaba abantu gukora cyangwa kuri Twitter?
Kuva mu 2011, Global Citizen ivuga ko imaze kubona "ibikorwa" birenga miliyoni 19 byakozwe n'abayoboke bayo, bashishikariza abantu gukora ibikorwa bitandukanye.
Ivuga ko abayobozi b'isi bamaze gutuma batangaza politiki n'imihigo bifite agaciro ka miliyari 37 z'amadolari, ayo politiki n'imihigo izagira ingaruka ku buzima bw'abantu barenga miliyari 2.25 mu mwaka wa 2030.
Mu ntangiriro z'umwaka wa 2018, iri tsinda ryatangaje amasezerano 390 n'ibyatangajwe byaturutse ku bikorwa, byibura miliyari 10 z'amadolari y'Amerika akaba yaramaze kwishyurwa cyangwa guhabwa.
Itsinda ryavuze ko amafaranga y'ingoboka yagize ingaruka ku bantu bagera kuri miliyoni 649 ku isi hose.
Mu by'ingenzi by'iri sezerano harimo The Power of Nutrition, "ishyirahamwe ry'abashoramari n'abashyira mu bikorwa, rifite icyicaro mu Bwongereza, ryiteguye gufasha abana kugera ku bushobozi bwabo", ryemeye gutanga miliyoni 35 z'amadolari mu Rwanda kugira ngo rifashe kurandura imirire mibi muri icyo gihugu, nyuma yo kwakira tweets zirenga 4,700 z'abaturage ba Global Citizens.
"Dufashijwe na guverinoma y'Ubwongereza, abaterankunga, guverinoma z'ibihugu n'abandi bagize Global Citizen nkawe, tugiye kureka akarengane k'imirire mibi mu mateka", uko ni ko ambasaderi wa The Power of Nutrition, Tracey Ullman, yabwiye abantu mu gitaramo cyabereye i Londres muri Mata 2018.
Ikindi kandi, iri tsinda ryavuze ko nyuma yo gukora ibikorwa birenga 5000 byo kunoza imirire y'ababyeyi n'abana mu Bwongereza, leta yatangaje ko igiye gutanga inkunga y'umushinga Power of Nutrition, umushinga uzaba ufasha abagore n'abana barenga miliyoni 5 binyuze mu ngamba zijyanye n'imirire.
Ku bijyanye n'igisubizo cya kimwe mu bibazo bikunze kubazwa ku rubuga rwabo, "Ni iki gituma wemera ko dushobora kurandura ubukene bukabije?"
Global Citizen yaranshubije iti "Ntabwo bizoroha, bizatugora, hari igihe tuzasitara, kandi tuzabura icyo dukora.
Ariko kimwe n'indi miryango ikomeye y'uburenganzira bwa muntu n'imiryango yamaganaga ivangura, tuzabishobora kuko dukomeye dufatanyije.
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B na Janelle Monáe, n'abandi benshi bazagaragara mu gitaramo kizabera i New York muri uyu mwaka, kizatangwa na Deborah-Lee Furness na Hugh Jackman.
Minisitiri w'Ubutegetsi bw'Igihugu ashobora gukoresha ingabo za Amerika mu guhagarika ibyo Uburusiya bukora mu bijyanye n'ingufu.
"Niba ari ngombwa, Washington ishobora gukoresha ingabo zayo mu guhagarika ingufu z'Uburusiya kugera ku masoko, harimo n'aya Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, "umunyamabanga w'ububanyi n'amahanga Ryan Zinke, nkuko byatangajwe na Washington Examiner.
Zinke yavuze ko umubano w'Uburusiya na Syria, aho bigaragara ko ubutegetsi bwemewe n'amategeko bukorera ku busabe bwabwo, ari urwitwazo rwo gushaka isoko rishya ry'ingufu.
"Ntekereza ko impamvu bari mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati ari uko bashaka gucuruza ingufu, nk'uko babikora mu Burayi bw'Iburasirazuba, mu nda y'amajyepfo y'u Burayi", ni ko yavuze, nk'uko bivugwa.
Nk'uko uwo muyobozi abivuga, hari uburyo n'uburyo bwo kubikemura.
Yagize ati "Amerika, ifatanyije n'Ingabo zacu, ifite ubushobozi bwo gutuma imiyoboro y'amazi iguma ifunguye, kandi niba ari ngombwa, no kuyikinga kugira ngo ikureho ingufu zayo ku isoko ryabo".
Zinke yari arimo kuvugana n'abitabiriye igikorwa cyateguwe n'ishyirahamwe ry'abakoresha ingufu, ni ukuvuga itsinda ry'imiryango idaharanira inyungu ryitangaza ko ari "ijwi ry'abakoresha ingufu" muri Amerika.
Washington yagereranyije uburyo bwayo bwo kubana n'Uburusiya n'ubwo kubana na Irani, maze isanga ari kimwe.
Yagize ati "Icyemezo cy'ubukungu dufata ku bijyanye na Irani n'Uburusiya, ni ugufata no gusimbuza ibyo bikoresho", avuga ko Uburusiya ari ubukungu "bwonyine" bushingiye ku bikoresho bya peteroli.
Ibyo bitangazo byatanzwe mu gihe ubutegetsi bwa Trump bufite intego yo guteza imbere ibyoherezwa by'ibikomoka kuri peteroli mu Burayi no kubisimbuza Uburusiya, uburyo buhendutse ku bakiriya b'i Burayi.
Kugira ngo ibyo bigerweho, abayobozi b'ubutegetsi bwa Trump, ndetse na Perezida wa Amerika Donald Trump ubwe, bagerageje kwemeza u Budage kuva mu mushinga wa gazi wa Nord Stream 2, umushinga mu magambo ya Trump, uhindura Berlin "imbohe" ya Moscou.
Moscou yakomeje kuvuga ko umushinga wa Nord Stream 2 w'amadolari miliyoni 11, uzongera inshuro ebyiri ubushobozi bw'umuyoboro uriho wa gaz, ugera kuri miliyari 110 za metero kibe, ari umushinga w'ubukungu gusa.
Kremlin ivuga ko Washington itemera uwo mushinga kubera impamvu z'ubukungu gusa, kandi ko ari urugero rw'uko nta butabera buhari.
"Ntekereza ko twemeranya ko ingufu zidakwiye kuba igikoresho cyo kotsa igitutu kandi ko abakiriya bagomba guhitamo ababaha ibicuruzwa", niko Minisitiri w'ingufu w'Uburusiya, Aleksandr Novak yavuze nyuma y'inama yagiranye n'umunyamabanga w'ingufu wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Rick Perry, mu kwezi kwa cyenda i Moscou.
Ibi byitabiriwe nabi n'Abadage, bemeza ko Amerika yiyemeje gukora uwo mushinga.
Ishyirahamwe rikomeye ry'inganda z'Abadage, FIDH, ryasabye Amerika kudashora mu bikorwa by'ingufu z'Ubwongereza no mu masezerano y'ubufatanye hagati ya Berlin na Moscou.
"Mfite ikibazo gikomeye iyo igihugu cya gatatu kibangamiye ingufu zacu", Dieter Kempf, umuyobozi w'ishyirahamwe ry'inganda z'Abadage (BDI), yavuze nyuma y'inama iherutse guhuza Angela Merkel, Kanceli w'Ubudage na Vladimir Putin, Perezida w'Uburusiya.
Elizabeth Warren "azitekerezaho cyane" kwiyamamaza mu matora ya 2020, nk'uko byatangajwe n'umusenateri wa Massachusetts.
Umusenateri Elizabeth Warren wo muri leta ya Massachusetts, kuri uyu wa gatandatu yavuze ko azitekerezaho cyane kwiyamamaza mu matora y'umukuru w'igihugu nyuma y'amatora yo mu mwaka wa 2019.
Mu kiganiro yagiranye n'abanyamakuru, Warren yemeje ko azitekerezaho ko azagenda mu matora.
Yagize ati "Igihe kirageze ngo abagore baze i Washington bagorore ubutegetsi bwacu bwasenyutse, kandi ibyo bisaba ko umugore aba ari we uba ari ku isonga".
Nyuma y'itariki ya 6 Ugushyingo, nzatekereza cyane niba naregura ku mwanya wa Perezida".
Warren yavuze kuri Donald Trump mu nzu y'inama, avuga ko "yari arimo kuyobora igihugu mu nzira itari yo".
Yagize ati "Mfite impungenge zikomeye ku byo Donald Trump arimo akorera demokarasi yacu".
Warren yanenze cyane Trump n'uwari ugiye kujya mu rukiko rw'ikirenga, Brett Kavanaugh.
Mu butumwa bwo kuri Twitter bwo kuwa gatanu, Warren yagize ati "biragaragara ko dukeneye iperereza rya FBI mbere yo gutora".
Ariko kandi, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku wa Kane bwagaragaje ko abenshi mu batoye Warren batemera ko agomba kwiyamamaza mu 2020.
48% by'abashakaga gutora muri Massachusetts bavuga ko uwo musenateri atagomba kwiyamamaza, nk'uko ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi mu bya politiki cya Kaminuza ya Suffolk/Boston Globe bubigaragaza.
Abaturage bagera kuri 32 ku ijana bavuze ko bashaka ko yiyamamaza.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko Deval Patrick, uwahoze ari Guverineri, afite icyizere cyo guhatanira umwanya wa Perezida, aho 38% bashyigikiye ko ashobora guhatanira umwanya wa Perezida, naho 48% bamwangiye.
Mu bandi bazwiho kuba bahatanira kuyobora Amerika mu 2020, harimo Visi Perezida Joe Biden na Senateri Bernie Sanders wa Vermont.
Biden yavuze ko azafata icyemezo mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko muri Mutarama, nkuko byatangajwe na Associated Press.
