Yafashwe ku wa Mbere nimugoroba ashinjwa ihohoterwa rikorerwa mu ngo.
"Kubera ibyo umuhungu wanjye arimo kunyuramo, ibyo arimo kunyuramo ubwo yagarutse, ndumva nsangiye ingaruka z'indwara z'indwara z'indwara z'ibikomere n'izindi miryango ihanganye n'uburwayi buterwa no kugaruka kw'abasirikare bacu", yabwiye abantu bari mu muhango wo gushyigikira Donald Trump i Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Palin yavuze ko ifatwa ry'uwo musirikare "ari ikintu gikomeye", avuga ko umuhungu we n'abandi bavuye mu ntambara "basubira iwabo bahindutse, bagarutse bakomeye, bibaza niba hari icyo bubaha igihugu cyabo nk'uko abandi basirikare babo n'abasirikare bo mu kirere n'abandi basirikare bose babibona".
Yafashwe ku wa mbere w'iki cyumweru i Wasilla, Alaska, ashinjwa icyaha cyo gufata ku ngufu umugore wo mu rugo, harimo n'icy'uko yari afite imbunda y'uburozi, nk'uko bivugwa n'umuvugizi wa Polisi ya Wasilla, Dan Bennett.
Leta 18 harimo na D.C. zashyigikiye ikibazo cy'ubuhungiro bushya.
Leta 18 n'Akarere ka Columbia bashyigikiye itegeko rishyiraho itegeko rishya rya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ribuza ubuhungiro abantu bahunga imitwe y'abanyarugomo cyangwa ihohoterwa rikorerwa mu ngo.
Abahagarariye ibihugu 18 n'uturere twabo bashyize ahagaragara itangazo ryo gushyigikira umutabazi w'umunyamahanga muri Washington DC, ku wa Gatanu, bahanganye n'igipolisi, nkuko NBC News yabitangaje.
Izina ry'umushinjacyaha mu rubanza Grace v. Sessions rwasohowe n'ishyirahamwe ry'uburenganzira bwa muntu muri Kanama rwarwanyaga politiki ya leta ntiryatangajwe.
Yavuze ko yasambanyijwe n'uwo bari barashakanye "n'abagize agatsiko ke k'abanyarugomo", ariko ku itariki ya 20 Nyakanga, abayobozi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika banze ko asaba ubuhungiro.
Yafatiwe muri Texas.
Abunganira Grace mu by'amategeko bavuze ko El Salvador, Honduras na Guatemala ari byo bihugu bitanga umubare munini w'abasaba ubuhungiro muri Amerika, kubera ko ari ibihugu bifite ibibazo by'amabandi n'ihohoterwa rikorerwa mu ngo.
Politiki nshya y'ubuhungiro muri Amerika yatumye icyemezo cyafashwe na Komisiyo y'Ubujurire ku Bimukira cy'Amerika cyemerera abimukira batagira ibyangombwa bahunga ihohoterwa ryo mu ngo gusaba ubuhungiro.
Karl Racine, umushinjacyaha mukuru w'akarere ka Columbia, mu itangazo ryashyizwe ahagaragara ku wa Gatanu, yavuze ko "urwego rushya rw'abapolisi rwirengagiza imyaka y'amategeko ya leta, federasiyo n'ay'amahanga".
"Amategeko ya leta avuga ko buri musabe ubuhungiro agomba guhabwa uburenganzira ashingiye ku bintu by'ingenzi n'imimerere y'isaba, kandi ko itegeko nk'iryo ryangiza iryo hame", ni ko itangazo ry'abashakashatsi ryasobanuye.
Byongeye kandi, abanyamategeko bavuze mu nyandiko ko politiki yo kwanga abimukira kwinjira mu gihugu yangiza ubukungu bwa Amerika, kubera ko abo bimukira baba bafite ibyago byinshi byo kuba ba rwiyemezamirimo kandi bakabona "umurimo bakeneye".
Muri Kamena, umushinjacyaha mukuru Jeff Sessions yategetse abacamanza bashinzwe abimukira kutazongera guha ubuhungiro abantu bahunga urugomo rwo mu ngo n'urw'amabandi.
"Amahungiro araboneka ku bantu bava mu gihugu cyabo kubera gutotezwa cyangwa gutinya ko bazafatwa kubera ubwoko, idini, ubwenegihugu cyangwa kuba mu itsinda runaka cyangwa ibitekerezo bya politiki", ni ko Sessions yavuze ubwo yatangazaga politiki ye ku ya 11 Kamena.
Ubuhunzi ubwabwo ntabwo bwarigeze buba igisubizo cy'ibibazo byose abantu bahura nabyo buri munsi ku isi, nubwo ibibazo byabo byaba bikomeye.
Imihati yo kurokora abantu ikomeje gushyirwa mu bikorwa i Palu, mu gihe umubare w'abapfuye wikubye kabiri, mu gihe abantu benshi baharanira kurokora abandi.
Abari bakiriho, bari mu kaga gakomeye cyane.
"Hari ibintu byinshi bihangayikisha", ni ko Risa Kusuma, umubyeyi w'imyaka 35 w'umugore, yavuze ubwo yari arimo aruhura umwana we w'umuhungu urwaye umuriro mu mujyi wa Palu warimbuwe n'intambara.
"Ambulance z'abarwayi ziza buri munota.
Nta mazi meza ahari".
Babonye abaturage bagaruka mu mazu yabo yasenyutse, batoragura ibintu byabo byatwikiriwe n'amazi, bagerageza gukiza ibyo bashoboraga kubona.
Abantu babarirwa mu magana barakomeretse, ibitaro byasenyutse mu gihe cy'umutingito wari ufite ubukana bwa 7.5, kandi birarengewe.
Bamwe mu bakomeretse, nka Dwi Haris, bari bafite umugongo n'amavi by'amaboko, bari baruhukiye hanze y'ibitaro bya gisirikare bya Palu. Abarwayi bavurirwaga hanze kubera imyigaragambyo ikomeje.
Amarira yamurenze mu maso igihe yavugaga uko yahuye n'umutingito ukomeye ubwo yari mu cyumba cye cy'ihoteli ari kumwe n'umugore we n'umukobwa we.
"Ntitwari dufite igihe cyo kwikiza.
Ndumva naramanutse nkagwa ku musenyi w'urukuta", Haris yabwiye Associated Press, yongeraho ko umuryango we wari mu mujyi mu bukwe.
"Numvise umugore wanjye arira asaba ubufasha, maze numva nta wongeye kuvuga.
Sinzi uko byagenze kuri we n'umukobwa we.
Ndizera ko nta cyo babaye".
Ambasaderi wa Amerika yashinje u Bushinwa "guhatana" binyuze mu kwamamaza
Nyuma y'aho ikinyamakuru cy'igihugu cy'Ubushinwa cyashyize itangazo ry'amapaji ane mu kinyamakuru cyo muri Amerika, ryamamaza inyungu z'ubucuruzi hagati y'Ubushinwa na Amerika, ambasaderi wa Amerika yashinje Beijing gukoresha itangazamakuru rya Amerika mu kwamamaza poropagande ye.
Perezida Donald Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, mu kinyamakuru cy'Ubushinwa, Des Moines Register, ikinyamakuru cya kabiri kigurishwa cyane muri Leta ya Iowa, yavuze ku nyongera y'amafaranga y'inyongera yishyuriwe ku wa Gatatu ushize, nyuma yo gushinja u Bushinwa gushaka kwivanga mu matora y'abadepite yo ku wa 6 Ugushyingo, ibyo Ubushinwa bubihakana.
Kuba Trump yarashinje Beijing kwivanga mu matora yo muri Amerika, ni ikimenyetso gikomeye cy'uko abayobozi ba Amerika babwiye Reuters ko ari ikindi gikorwa cy'i Washington cyo gukangisha u Bushinwa.
Nubwo ari ibisanzwe ko za guverinoma z'amahanga zishyiriraho amatangazo agamije guteza imbere ubucuruzi, ariko ubu Beijing na Washington biri mu ntambara y'ubucuruzi igenda irushaho gukomera, aho buri gihugu gifata ibicuruzwa byacyo byose.
Abahanga mu by'Ubushinwa n'Amerika bavuga ko imyigaragambyo yo kwihorera y'u Bushinwa yari igamije guhungabanya ibyoherezwa mu mahanga n'ibihugu nka Iowa, byafashije ishyaka ry'aba-Republican rya Trump mu ntangiriro z'intambara y'ubucuruzi.
Terry Branstad, ambasaderi wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika mu Bushinwa, akaba n'umuyobozi w'intara ya Iowa umaze igihe kirekire, ari na yo leta yo mu zindi z'Amerika zikorera mu Bushinwa, yavuze ko Beijing yangije cyane abakozi, abahinzi n'ubucuruzi muri Amerika.
Branstad yanditse mu kinyamakuru cyo ku Cyumweru cyo muri Des Moines Register, avuga ko "Ubushinwa buri kongera igitero cyabwo bushyira amatangazo yo kwamamaza mu binyamakuru byacu byigenga".
Branstad yaranditse ati "mu gukwirakwiza poropagande, guverinoma y'Ubushinwa ikoresha umuco ukomeye w'itangazamakuru ry'ubwisanzure muri Amerika n'ubwisanzure mu itangazamakuru, ishyiraho amatangazo y'ibyamamare kuri Des Moines Register".
"Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, mu kinyamakuru cyo ku muhanda hano i Beijing, hari amajwi make y'abatavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi, kandi nta kintu kigaragaza mu buryo nyabwo ibitekerezo bitandukanye abaturage b'u Bushinwa bashobora kuba bafite ku nzira y'ubukungu y'ibibazo, aho itangazamakuru rigengwa n'ubuyobozi bukomeye bw'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'u Bushinwa", ni ko yanditse.
Yongeyeho ko "kimwe mu binyamakuru bikomeye byo mu Bushinwa cyirengagije gutanga ikiganiro cye", ariko ntiyavuze icyo kinyamakuru.
Abarepubulikani batumye abagore batinya gutora mbere y'amatora yo mu mwaka wa kabiri w'ubutegetsi bwa Perezida, kubera ko Kavanaugh yaguye mu mutego, nk'uko abahanga babivuga.
Mu gihe abarepubulikani benshi bakomeye bategereje ko Brett Kavanaugh, umukandida w'urukiko rw'ikirenga, azajya mu butabera nyuma yo gushinjwa ihohoterwa rishingiye ku gitsina, abahanga baraburira ko bashobora kwitega ko umubare w'abaperezida, cyane cyane abagore, uzagenda ugabanuka mu matora yo mu mwaka wa 2019.
Umwuka w'amacakubiri kuri iki kibazo wari mwinshi cyane, kandi abenshi mu Burepubulikani bari biyandikishije bagaragaza ko bifuza ko ayo matora akomeza.
Ibyo bintu ntaho ushobora kubisubiza inyuma", Grant Reeher, umwarimu mu ishuri rya Maxwell muri kaminuza ya Syracuse yabwiye The Hill ku nkuru yasohotse ku wa Gatandatu.
Reeher yavuze ko ashidikanya ko igitutu cya Sena ya Arizona, Jeff Flake, cy'uko leta y'Amerika yashyigikira iperereza rya FBI, kizaba gihagije kugira ngo gishimishe abatora bari barakaye.
"Abagore ntibazibagirwa ibyabaye ejo - ntibazibagirwa ejo, kandi ntibazibagirwa mu Ugushyingo", ni ko Karine Jean-Pierre, umujyanama mukuru akaba n'umuvugizi w'itsinda ry'abahanga mu iterambere rya MoveOn, yavuze, nk'uko byatangajwe n'ikinyamakuru cyo muri Washington, D.C.
Mu gitondo cyo kuwa gatanu, abigaragambya baririmbaga bati "Ugushyingo uraje!" bari mu myigaragambyo imbere y'inteko ishinga amategeko y'inteko ishinga amategeko y'Amerika, bavuga ko abarepubulikani bari bayoboye komite y'ubutabera, bahisemo gukomeza gushyiraho Kavanaugh nubwo Dr. Christine Blasey Ford yari ahari.
"Umushinga n'impamvu by'abademokarate ntibizongera kubaho", uko ni ko Stu Rothenberg, umuhanga mu bya politiki wigenga yabwiye urubuga rw'amakuru.
Ati "Abantu bavuga ko yagize ingaruka; ni ukuri.
Ariko bishobora no kugira ingaruka zikomeye cyane cyane ku bagore bo mu nkengero z'umugi n'urubyiruko rw'abantu bafite imyaka iri hagati ya 18 na 29, badafite uburyo bwo gutora, kubera ko nubwo badakunda perezida, akenshi ntibatora".
Mbere y'uko Ford atanga ubuhamya ku mugaragaro ku byerekeye ihohoterwa rishingiye ku gitsina yakoreye uwari ugiye kuyobora Urukiko rw'Ikirenga, abahanga bavuze ko bishobora kuba ari ugutaha niba Abarepubulikani bahisemo gukomeza.
"Byabaye akajagari gakomeye mu ishyaka ry'aba Repubulika", Michael Steele, uwahoze ayobora Komite y'Igihugu y'Aba Repubulika, yavuze mu ntangiriro z'icyumweru gishize, nk'uko NBC News yabitangaje.
Umuyobozi w'itsinda ry'abademokarate ryita ku matora rya "Priorities USA" yabwiye ikinyamakuru cya BBC ati "Ikibazo si uko komite y'amatora, amajwi ya nyuma, cyangwa niba Kavanaugh agomba kwicara mu cyumba cy'abashinjwa, ahubwo ni uburyo abarepubulikani bakemuye iki kibazo n'uburyo bafata uyu mugore".
Ariko kandi, Abanyamerika basa n'abaciwe amajwi hagati y'ibyo Ford n'uwitwa Kavanaugh bavuga ku birebana n'uwo bemera, ariko abantu benshi basa n'abemera ibyo avuga.
Ubushakashatsi bushya bwakozwe na YouGov bwagaragaje ko 41% by'ababajijwe bemeraga rwose cyangwa byanze bikunze ubuhamya bwa Ford, naho 35% bemera rwose cyangwa byanze bikunze ubuhamya bwa Kavanaugh.
Byongeye kandi, 38% bavuze ko batekereza ko Kavanaugh ashobora kuba yarabeshye cyangwa ko ashobora kuba yarabeshye mu buhamya bwe, naho 30% bavuga ko ibyo ari ukuri ku byerekeye Ford.
Nyuma y'igitutu cya Flake, ibirego bya Ford ubu biri gukorwaho iperereza na FBI, ndetse n'ibindi by'umwe mu bashinjacyaha, Deborah Ramirez, nkuko The Guardian yabitangaje.
Mu cyumweru gishize, Ford yatanze ubuhamya imbere y'akanama k'ubutabera ka Sena ko Ford yateye Kavanaugh yasinze ubwo yari afite imyaka 17.
Ramirez avuga ko uwari ugiye kuba umucamanza w'urukiko rw'ikirenga yamweretse ibice by'ibitsina bye mu birori bari bafite igihe bari abanyeshuri muri Yale mu myaka ya za 80.
Uwatangije World Wide Web avuga ko agiye gutangiza interineti nshya izarwanya Google na Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, umuhanga mu guhanga imbuga nkoranyambaga, arashaka gutangiza ikigo gitangira ubucuruzi kigamije guhatana na Facebook, Amazon na Google.
Umushinga wa nyuma w'umuhanga mu ikoranabuhanga, Inrupt, ni isosiyete ishingiye kuri porogaramu y'ubuntu ya Solid ya Berners-Lee.
Solid ituma abakoresha bahitamo aho amakuru yabo abikwa n'abazabasha kuyabona.
Mu kiganiro cyihariye na Fast Company, Berners-Lee yatwenze avuga ko umugambi wa Inrupt ari "gufata isi".
Yagize ati "Tugomba kubikora ubu".
"Iki ni igihe cy'amateka".
Porogaramu ikoresha ikoranabuhanga rya Solid kugirango abantu bashobore gukora "ububiko bwabo bwite bw'amakuru bwite" cyangwa POD.
Ishobora kuba irimo urutonde rw'abantu, urutonde rw'ibyo ugomba gukora, kalendari, umuziki n'ibindi bikoresho bya bwite n'ibya kinyamwuga.
Ni nka Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack na Spotify: byose biri kumwe muri mushakisha imwe, byose icyarimwe.
Ikintu cyihariye kububiko bwibuntu kumurongo ni uko bigarukira rwose kumukoresha ni nde ushobora kubona amakuru runaka.
Icyo kigo cyitwa "guha abantu ububasha binyuze mu makuru".
Nk'uko umuyobozi mukuru John Bruce abivuga, igitekerezo kiri inyuma ya Inrupt ni ugushyira hamwe ibikoresho, inzira n'ubushobozi bikwiye kugira ngo umuntu wese ashobore gukoresha Solid.
Ubu iyi sosiyete igizwe na Berners-Lee, Bruce, urubuga rw'umutekano rwigaruriwe na IBM, bamwe mu bashakashatsi bahembwe gukora kuri uyu mushinga n'umuryango w'abakozi bitangiye gukora porogaramu.
Guhera kuri iki cyumweru, abahanga mu ikoranabuhanga ku isi hose bashobora gukora porogaramu zabo bwite zidakoreshwa bakoresheje ibikoresho biboneka ku rubuga rwa Inrupt.
Berners-Lee yavuze ko we n'itsinda rye batavugana na Facebook na Google ku mpamvu bagomba guhindura ibintu mu buryo bugaragara igihe imikorere yabo ihindutse mu buryo bugaragara mu ijoro rimwe.
"Ntitubasaba uruhushya".
Mu butumwa bwashyizwe kuri Medium kuwa gatandatu, Berners-Lee yanditse ko Inrupt "ari inshingano yo gushyiraho ikoranabuhanga n'imbaraga z'ubucuruzi bizafasha kurinda ubuziranenge n'ubwiza bw'urusobe rushya rwubatswe muri Solid".
Mu 1994, Berners-Lee yahinduye internet igihe yashingaga World Wide Web Consortium muri Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
Mu mezi make ashize, Berners-Lee yagaragaye nk'ijwi rifite imbaraga mu mpaka zivuga ku kutabogama kwa Internet.
Ndetse no mugihe cyo gutangiza Inrupt, Berners-Lee azakomeza kuba umwanditsi washinze akaba n'umuyobozi wa World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation na Open Data Institute.
Berners-Lee yongeyeho ati "Ndi umuntu witeze ko ibintu bizagenda neza mu gihe kizaza cya interineti".
Bernard Vann, umuyobozi w'idini w'Umunyamerika, yahembwe n'Igikombe cya Victoria cyo mu Ntambara ya Mbere y'Isi Yose
Umupadiri wa Kiliziya y'Ubwongereza wenyine wahawe igihembo cy'Igikombe cya Victoria nk'umusirikare mu ntambara ya mbere y'isi yose, mu myaka 100 ishize, mu mujyi we w'iwabo, habaye umuhango wo guha icyubahiro uwo mupadiri.
Lt. Colonel Bernard Vann, ku itariki ya 29 Nzeri 1918, yatsindiye igihembo cye mu gitero cya Bellenglise na Lehaucourt.
Ariko yaje kwicwa n'umusirikare w'umunyamurenge nyuma y'iminsi ine, kandi ntiyigeze amenya ko yahawe igihembo cy'icyubahiro cya gisirikare cyo mu Bwongereza.
Ibuye ry'urwibutso ryatangajwe n'abuzukuru be babiri mu birori byo kwibuka i Rushden, Northamptonshire, ku wa Gatandatu w'icyumweru gishize.
Umwe mu buzukuru be, Michael Vann, yavuze ko "ari ikimenyetso gikomeye" kuba iryo buye ryarerekanywe nyuma y'imyaka 100 sekuru we ahawe igihembo.
Nk'uko byavuzwe mu kinyamakuru cy'i Londres, ku itariki ya 29 Nzeri 1918, Lt. Col. Vann yayoboye umutwe we w'abasirikare banyura mu mugezi wa Saint-Quentin, bari mu gace k'ibishanga, kandi barashwe n'imbunda n'imbunda.
Nyuma yaje kwihuta ajya ku murongo wa mbere w'umuriro, maze abigiranye ubutwari bwinshi ayobora umurongo imbere kugeza ubwo ahuriye n'imbunda we wenyine kandi arayijugunya ku butaka butatu bw'itsinda rye.
Lt. Col. Vann yishwe n'umucunguzi w'Umudage ku itariki ya 4 Ukwakira 1918, hasigaye ukwezi kumwe ngo intambara irangire.
Michael Vann w'imyaka 72, yavuze ko yari azi ibikorwa bya sekuru "atari kuzigera na rimwe abikora, ariko byatuma yicisha bugufi cyane".
We na musaza we, Dr. James Vann, bashyize indabo ku birenge byaho nyuma y'iri serukiramuco, riyobowe n'itsinda ry'abasore b'abami b'i Brentwood.
Michael Vann yavuze ko "yari afite icyubahiro cyo kwitabira iyi paradizo" yongeraho ko "gushyigikira abantu benshi bigaragaza ubutwari bw'intwari nyakuri".
Abakunzi ba MMA bari bategereje ijoro ryose kureba Bellator 206, ariko bahise bahitamo Peppa Pig.
Reka tuvuge ko waraye usinziriye ijoro ryose ureba ikiganiro cya Bellator 206 cyuzuye abantu, hanyuma bakakubuza kureba igice cy'ingenzi.
San Jose yahagaritse imikino 13 muri yo, harimo imikino 6 yo mu minsi mikuru ikomeye, kandi yagombaga gutambuka kuri Channel 5 mu Bwongereza.
Saa kumi n'ebyiri za mu gitondo, ubwo Gegard Mousasi na Rory MacDonald bari mu myitozo yo guhangana, abarebye mu Bwongereza baratangaye ubwo bahinduraga ikiganiro cya televiziyo bakitwa Peppa Pig.
Bamwe muri bo ntibatangajwe n'uko bari barinze babyuka mu gitondo cya kare, bitegura kurwana.
Umwe mu bakurikiraga Twitter yavuze ko "ihinduka rya Twitter ku bitabo by'abana ari urwenya rw'urukozasoni".
"Itegeko rya guverinoma rivuga ko ibi bikubiyemo bitari bikwiriye saa kumi n'ebyiri za mu gitondo, bityo byabaye ngombwa ko bahindura ibiganiro by'abana", Dave Schwartz, Visi Perezida Mukuru w'Ubucuruzi n'Itumanaho kuri Bellator, ubwo yabazwaga ku kiganiro.
"Peppa, ingurube, yego".
Scott Coker, umuyobozi wa Bellator, yavuze ko mu gihe kiri imbere, bazakora ubushakashatsi ku biganiro by'abanyamakuru kugira ngo barebe abareba mu Bwongereza.
Coker yagize ati "Ntekereza ko iyo ntekereje ku gusubiramo, numva ko bishoboka ko dushobora kubikemura".
"Ariko ni ku cyumweru saa kumi n'ebyiri za mu gitondo, kandi nta cyo twakora kugeza ku cyumweru ku isaha yacu, kuwa mbere ku isaha yabo.
Ariko turimo turakora ku kibazo.
Kandi munyizere, igihe impinduka zabaga, nabonaga ubutumwa bwinshi cyane, kandi bwose ntibwishimishije.
Twagerageje kubikemura ariko dutekereza ko ari ikibazo cy'ikoranabuhanga.
Ariko si byo. Ni ibintu bya leta.
Ndabizeza ko ubutaha bitazongera.
Tuzashyiraho imikino itanu aho kuba itandatu nk'uko bisanzwe, twagerageje guha abantu amafaranga menshi ariko twarabishe.
Ni ibintu bibabaje cyane".
"Igitsina cy'abantu benshi"
Tom Daley, umusare wa Olempike, avuga ko yakuriye mu mimerere yo kumva ko asuzuguritse bitewe n'imibonano mpuzabitsina, ariko ko ibyo byatumye agira imbaraga zo kugira icyo ageraho.
Uyu mugabo w'imyaka 24 yavuze ko kugeza ageze mu mashuri yisumbuye ari bwo yamenye ko "abantu bose batari nka we".
Mu kiganiro cya mbere cya Desert Island Discs cyatambutse kuri Radio 4, Lauren Laverne yavuze ko yavugaga ku burenganzira bw'abatinganyi kugira ngo aha abandi "ibyiringiro".
Yongeyeho ko kuba umubyeyi byatumye atita cyane ku gutsinda imikino Olempike.
Uwari umaze igihe kirekire ari umuyobozi wa "The Voice", Kirsty Young, yemeye kujya mu kiruhuko cy'amezi menshi kubera uburwayi.
Nyuma yo kugaragara nk'uwataye ubwenge mu kiganiro cya mbere cya Laverne, Daley yavuze ko yumvaga "asuzuguritse" ugereranyije n'abandi bose kubera ko umuryango utemera ko abantu bakunda abahungu n'abakobwa".
Yagize ati "Kugeza ubu, ibintu bituma wumva ko uri hasi kandi utandukanye n'abandi, ni byo byampaye imbaraga n'ubushobozi bwo kugira icyo ngeraho".
Yashakaga kugaragaza ko hari ikintu runaka mu buzima bwe, kuko yavuze ko atifuzaga ko abantu bamubera ibamba igihe bari kuba bamenye imiterere ye y'ibitsina.
Uyu mukinnyi watsindiye imidari ibiri y'umuringa mu mikino ya Olempike yabaye umuyobozi ukomeye wa LGBT, kandi yakoresheje uruhare rwe mu mikino ya Commonwealth muri Ositaraliya asaba ibihugu byinshi kuvanaho ubuhehesi.
Yavuze ko yahisemo kuvuga ibyo kuko yumvaga afite amahirwe yo kubaho mu bwisanzure nta ngaruka z'ibyo bintu, kandi ashaka guha abandi "ibyiringiro".
Uyu mugabo wari umaze kuba shampiyona y'isi inshuro eshatu yavuze ko kuba yarakundanye n'umugabo - Dustin Lance Black, umuhanzi w'umunyamerika wamenyanye mu mwaka wa 2013 - "byamutangaje cyane".
Mu mwaka ushize, Daley yashyingiranywe n'umukinnyi wa Oskar umurutaho imyaka 20, ariko avuga ko itandukaniro ry'imyaka ridakomeje kuba ikibazo hagati yabo.
Yagize ati "iyo ukiri muto cyane kandi ibintu byinshi bikakubaho" - yagiye mu mikino Olempike bwa mbere afite imyaka 14, se apfa na kanseri imyaka itatu nyuma yaho - biragoye kubona umuntu mu kigero cye wigeze ahura n'ibintu nk'ibyo.
Aba bombi baje kubyara umwana witwa Robert Ray Black-Daley muri Kamena, kandi Daley yavuze ko "imyumvire ye yose" yarahindutse.
Yagize ati "iyo unyibaza umwaka ushize, ikintu cyonyine nari mfite mu bwenge bwanjye cyari 'Ngiye gutsinda umudali wa zahabu.'"
Ati "Kandi, urabizi, hari ibintu bifite agaciro kurusha imidari ya zahabu mu mikino ya Olempiki.
Robbie ni we munyazahabu wanjye wa Olempike".
Umuhungu we yitwa nka se Robert, yapfuye mu 2011 afite imyaka 40 nyuma yo gusangwamo kanseri y'ubwonko.
Daley yavuze ko se atigeze yemera ko yari agiye gupfa, kandi ko kimwe mu bintu bya nyuma yasabye ari uko bamuha amatike yo kujya mu mikino y'i Londres mu mwaka wa 2012, kuko yifuzaga cyane kujya mu murongo wa mbere.
Yagize ati "sinashoboraga kumubwira ko utazashobora kwicara mu murongo wa mbere, papa".
Yagize ati "Nari mfashe ukuboko kwe igihe yari aretse guhumeka, kandi kugeza igihe yaretse guhumeka, maze agapfa, ni bwo numvise ko atari akwiriye kuneshwa".
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho Daley yitabiriye imikino Olempike ya 2012, aho yatsindiye umudali wa zahabu.
Yagize ati "nari nzi ko ari byo nari nararose mu buzima bwanjye bwose, kuba imbere y'abantu benshi mu mikino Olempike, nta kindi kintu nabonaga kiruta icyo".
Yongeyeho ko byamuteye guhitamo indirimbo ye ya mbere - Proud, ya Heather Small - yatumye yumva ko yamenyekanye mu gihe cyose cyo kwitegura imikino Olempike kandi ikomeje kumutera ubwoba.
Desert Island Discs itangwa kuri BBC Radio 4 ku cyumweru saa kumi n'imwe n'iminota 15 ku isaha y'i Burayi.
Mickelson, wari utari mu buryo bwiza, yari yicaye ku ntebe ku mukino wa Ryder Cup ku wa Gatandatu.
Umunyamerika Phil Mickelson azakora umukino wa 47 w'igikombe cya Ryder ku cyumweru, ariko azakomeza gukina kugira ngo atazaboneka nabi.
Mickelson yari amaze imyaka ibiri ahimba umukino wa 12 mu mukino umwe, ariko yaje guhanwa na kapiteni we Jim Fury mu mikino ya Fourball na Foursome yo ku wa Gatandatu.
Aho kugira ngo abe mu mwanya w'ibanze w'ibikorwa, nk'uko yagiye abikora kenshi ku ruhande rwa Amerika, uyu mugabo w'imyaka itanu w'umunyabigwi muri Grand Prix, yagabanyije umunsi we aba umukinnyi w'indirimbo zishimishije, kandi akora ku mukino ku kibuga, yizeye gukosora ibimubabaza.
Ntabwo yigeze aba umushoferi uhamye, ndetse no mu bihe byiza by'akazi ke, kandi uyu mugabo w'imyaka 48 ntabwo ari ihitamo ryiza ku buryo yabasha guhatanira guhatanira igikombe cya Le Golf National, aho abakinnyi bakomeye cyane ari bo bigarurira abatsinzwe.
Kandi nubwo ikibuga ubwacyo kitari ikintu giteye ubwoba, Mickelson, mu mukino wa cyenda ku cyumweru, azahura na Francesco Molina, nyampinga wa British Open, wafatanyije na Tommy Fleetwood, umukinnyi mushya, mu gutsinda imikino ine muri iki cyumweru.
Niba Abanyamerika batangiye imikino 12 yose bari munsi y'amanota ane, kandi bakomeza gutangira neza, umukino wa Mickelson ushobora kuba umukino ukomeye.
Fury yemeye ko umugabo we yari afite ubushobozi bwo kumubwira byinshi.
"Yari asobanukiwe neza inshingano yari afite uyu munsi, maze arankoma ku mugongo, maze ambwira ko azayisohoza ejo", Fury yagize ati "n'ejo bundi nzayisohoza".
"Ni umuntu wifitiye icyizere.
Ni umukinnyi ukomeye kandi yakoze ibintu byinshi muri iyi kipe, haba mu gihe cyashize no muri iki cyumweru.
Birashoboka ko ntari kubona umukino wa kabiri.
Nari niteze ko ibintu byagenda neza, ariko ni ko byagenze. Kandi ni ko twabonye ko ari byo twagombaga gukora.
Yifuza kuba muri uwo murimo, kimwe n'abandi bose".
Mickelson azatsinda agahigo ka Nick Faldo ko kuba umukinnyi w'igikombe cya Ryder ufite imyaka myinshi ku cyumweru.
Ibi bishobora kuba ari iherezo ry'umukino wa Ryder Cup, aho uyu mugabo atazongera kugera ku manota ye y'umuntu ku giti cye.
Mickelson yatsinze inshuro 18, atsindwa inshuro 18, atsindwa inshuro 7, ariko Furyke avuga ko yazanye ikintu kitabasha gukorwako.
Ati "Afite uburyo bwo guseka, ni umunyarugomo kandi ni umunyabwenge, akunda gusetsa abantu kandi kuba ahari ni byiza".
"Abakinnyi bato bishimiye gukina na we muri iki cyumweru, kandi byari bishimishije kumureba.
Nta kindi akora uretse gukina urusimbi".
Thomas Bjorn kapiteni w'ikipe y'u Burayi azi ko imbere yabo hashobora guhita hasenyuka.
Thomas Bjorn, kapiteni w'ikipe y'u Burayi, azi ko nubwo afite imbere mu mukino w'umunsi wa nyuma, igikombe cya Ryder gishobora guhinduka imimerere ibabaje.
Mu 1997, uyu mukinnyi w'icyamamare w'umunya-Danemark yatangiye mu mukino wa Valderrama, aho ikipe ye yari iyobowe na Seve Ballesteros yari ifite amanota atanu imbere y'Abanyamerika, ariko batsinze igikombe ku munota wa 141⁄2 na 131⁄2.
"Nihora nibutsa ko twari dufite imbere ikomeye i Valderrama kandi twatsinze ku mubyimba, kandi twaratsinzwe i Brooklyn nubwo twari dufite imbere ikomeye", Bjorn (afotowe) yavuze nyuma yo gutsinda Class ya 2018 ibitego 5-3 kuwa gatanu no ku munsi w'ejo, dufite imbere 10-6 kuri Le Golf National.
Amateka aratubwira, jyewe n'abandi bose turi mu itsinda, ko ibi bitararangira.
Tuzagira icyo dukora ejo.
Tuzajya mu kibuga, tugerageze gukora ibintu neza.
Nta kintu na kimwe cyemejwe kugeza igihe ibyo bintu bizaba byanditswe ku kibaho.
Tugiye gutsinda igikombe, kandi icyo ni cyo twifuza.
Nk'uko nabisobanuye, nitaye ku bakinnyi 12 turi kumwe, ariko tuzi neza abo turi kumwe, bamwe mu bakinnyi beza ku isi".
Bjorn, ashimishwa n'ibyo abakinnyi be bagezeho ku kibuga cya golf kitoroshye, yagize ati "sinigeze nifuza ko hagira ikintu na kimwe cyihutirwa.
Ni umunsi w'ejo.
Ejo ni umunsi w'abakinnyi babiri, kandi ibyo ni ibindi bindi.
Ni byiza kugira umufasha mu gihe ibintu bigenda neza, ariko iyo uri wenyine, umukinnyi wa golf wese aba agomba kugaragaza ubushobozi bwe bwose.
Icyo ni cyo tugiye kubwira abakinnyi bacu, nimukore uko mushoboye ejo hazaza.
Noneho, wibagirwe ko abo mufatanyije umurimo bose bagomba gukora uko bashoboye kose kugira ngo bagire icyo bageraho".
Bitandukanye na Bjorn, Jim Fury wo mu ikipe bahanganye na we yemeza ko abakinnyi be bose bazaba beza kurusha uko bari ku giti cyabo, uretse Jordan Spieth na Justin Thomas, bafite amanota atatu kuri ane.
Fury ubwe yari ku mpande zombi z'iyo mpinduka y'imikorere mu minsi ya nyuma, nk'umwe mu bagize ikipe yatsinze i Brooklyn, hanyuma nyuma yaho, itsindwa n'ikipe y'i Burayi, ubwo Abanyaburayi bakoze icyo bise "Igitangaza cy'i Medine".
"Nzi neza amagambo yose yavuze", ni ko yavuze igihe twabazaga Ben Crenshawk wari kapiteni w'ikipe mu 1999 uko yashyigikiye abakinnyi ku munsi wa nyuma w'umukino.
Ati "Dufite imikino 12 ikomeye ejo, ariko twifuza gukomeza kugira amahirwe nk'uko twabikoreye i Brooklyn n'i Medina.
Iyo uwari uhagarariye undi afite imbaraga, hari igitutu kinini mu mikino yo hagati.
Twahisemo dukurikije urutonde rw'abakinnyi, kandi twizeye ko tuzakora akazi keza ejo".
Thomas afite akazi ko kwishyura, kandi azatsinda Rory McIlroy mu mukino wa nyuma, Paul Casey, Justin Rose, Jon Rahm, Tommy Fleetwood na Ian Poulter, abandi banyamerika bo mu cyiciro cyo hejuru cyo hagati.
Bjorn yavuze ko "natoranyije abo bantu muri gahunda nk'iyo, kuko bari mu mimerere yo gukora urugendo rwose".
