Ariko kubera gutinda guhoraho, amato y'intambara afite ikoranabuhanga rigezweho (ari yo Ubudage bugamije kwerekana imbaraga zabwo) azasaza igihe azinjira mu bikorwa, nkuko ikinyamakuru Die Zeit kibivuga.
F125 yari yarangije nabi cyane mu mwaka ushize, yatumye itangazamakuru rivuga cyane, ubwo ingabo z'Abadage zamaganaga ku mugaragaro ibisabwa kuri ubwo bwato, maze busubizwa mu kigo cy'ubwubatsi cy'amato cya Blohm & Voss i Hamburg.
Ni ubwa mbere ubwato bw'abasirikare b'inyanja bwasubiye mu bwato bw'ubwubatsi nyuma yo gutanga.
Impamvu z'iyo mpinduka ntiziramenyekana, ariko itangazamakuru ry'Abadage ryavuze ko "amakosa akomeye ya software na hardware" yatumye ubwato butabasha gukoreshwa mu butumwa bw'intambara.
Ubwato bw'ubwoko bwa Baden-Wuerttemberg buzakoreshwa n'abasare 120, kimwe cya kabiri cyabo bakorera ku mato y'ubwoko bwa Bremen.
Byongeye kandi, ubwato buremerewe cyane kandi ibyo bituma imikorere yabwo igabanuka cyane, kandi biragoye ko abasirikare b'inyanja bongeramo udushya mugihe kizaza.
Ubwato bwa toni 7000 bwitwa Rheinland-Pfalz, buremereye inshuro ebyiri z'ubwato bw'ubwoko nk'ubwo bwakoreshejwe n'Abadage mu ntambara ya kabiri y'isi yose.
Usibye ibikoresho byangiritse, igiciro cyumushinga wose (harimo no guhugura abakozi) ni ikibazo.
Bivugwa ko byageze kuri miliyari 3,1 z'amayero, ku mafaranga 2,200 yari yagombaga gutangwa.
Ibibazo by'izo ngabo nshya byongereweho n'ibimenyetso by'uko ingabo z'Abadage zigiye kugabanuka.
Mu mezi make ashize, Hans-Peter Bartels, uyobora komite y'ingabo mu nteko ishinga amategeko y'u Budage, yemeye ko amato y'ingabo z'intambara arimo arashira.
Uwo mudepite yavuze ko ikibazo cyongereweho ikibazo cy'ubushomeri, kubera ko amato ashaje atajya asimburwa n'andi.
Yatangaje ko nta bwato na bumwe bw'ubwoko bwa Baden-Wuerttemberg bwigeze buhabwa ubwato bw'intambara.
Ubuzima bw'ibanga bw'imbeba bwashyizwe mu cyubahiro n'ikigo cy'igihugu cyita ku buzima.
Ubushakashatsi bushya bwakozwe ku kibanza kiri mu misozi yo muri Ecosse, bugamije kumenya uko udusimba dukoresha ubutaka mu gushakisha ibiryo.
Biteganyijwe ko bazamenya byinshi ku myitwarire y'izo nyamaswa z'ibiguruka zihariye, bityo mu gihe kiri imbere bazabona uburyo bwo kuzirinda.
Ubushakashatsi bukorwa n'abahanga mu by'ubumenyi bo muri Scottish National Trust (NTS) buzakomeza gukurikirana inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa common dwarf bat na soprano, ndetse n'inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa big-eared na Daubenton bat, mu busitani bwa Inverewe mu ntara ya Wester Ross.
Hari ibikoresho byo gufata amajwi bizashyirwa ahantu h'ingenzi kugira ngo bikurikirane ibikorwa by'izo nkozi z'ibibi mu gihe cyose cy'umwaka.
Abakozi bo mu kigo cy'ubuzima cya NHS cyo mu Bwongereza, bazongera bakore ubuvumbuzi bw'ibikoresho by'indengakamere bikoreshwa mu kugorora.
Igihe abahanga bazasesengura amajwi y'ibi bikoresho byose, bazamenya uko ibyo birura by'imbeba byumvikana n'ibyo buri bwoko bukora.
Nyuma yaho, hazakorwa ikarita y'aho ibarizwa n'ibikoresho byo kugenzura kugira ngo haboneke ishusho y'imyifatire y'izo nyamanswa.
Rob Dewar, umujyanama w'ibidukikije muri NTS, yavuze ko ibi bizagaragaza ahantu habereye ingo z'ingurube, n'uburyo buri bwoko bukoresha.
Aya makuru azatuma hamenyekana ibyiza byo kwita ku bibano, nko kubumbatira ibyatsi, nuburyo bwiza bwo kubungabunga amashyamba ku myunzu n'amoko afitanye isano nayo.
Umubare w'imbeba zo muri Écosse no mu Bwongereza wose waragabanutse cyane mu kinyejana gishize.
Bafite ibyago byinshi byo kubura aho baba bitewe n'ubwubatsi, ibyo bikaba byangiza aho baba n'aho baba.
Mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo, abantu benshi bavuga ko ari abantu bafite ubushobozi bwo kwihanganira ibyago, ariko ibyo ntibisobanura ko ari bo bonyine babikemura.
Mu by'ukuri, udusimba ntiduhuma.
Ariko kandi, kubera ko ubusanzwe iyo nyamaswa irya nijoro, amatwi yayo ni yo abafasha cyane mu guhiga inyamaswa.
Bakoresha uburyo bwo kumenya aho indege iri, kugira ngo bamenye inzitizi n'ibipfunsi biri mu nzira y'indege.
NTS ifite imiterere y'inyubako 270 z'amateka, ubusitani 38 bw'ingenzi na hegitari 76,000 muri Scotland, kandi ifata udusimba mu buryo bukomeye.
Abafite abahanga 10 batojwe, bakora igenzura, gusuzuma ibigo, ndetse rimwe na rimwe no gutabara.
Mu by'ukuri, ikigo cyashyizeho ahantu ha mbere kandi honyine habatse udukoko two mu bwoko bwa bat muri Scotland mu gace ka Threave muri Dumfries na Galloway, aho hari amoko umunani muri icumi y'udukoko two mu bwoko bwa bat muri Scotland.
David Thompson, umuyobozi w'ako gace, yavuze ko ako gace ari ko gahebuje ku buryo bashoboraga kuhatura.
Yagize ati "Turafite ahantu heza ho kuryamira udusimba mu mujyi wa Threaven".
Ati "Dufite inyubako zishaje n'ibiti bimaze imyaka myinshi, ni ahantu heza cyane ho kuba.
Ariko kandi, hari byinshi tutaramenya ku byerekeye udukoko, bityo rero, binyuze mu kazi dukora hano no mu tundi duce, tugiye gusobanukirwa icyo dukeneye kugira ngo dukomeze kuba bazima".
Thompson yavuze ko ari ngombwa cyane kugenzura niba hari udusimba mbere yo gukora ibikorwa byo kubungabunga ku butaka kuko iyo ikibuno kimwe cy'indaro cyangiritse, udusimba 400 tw'ingore n'utw'abana dushobora gupfa, ndetse wenda n'abaturage bose bo muri ako gace bashobora kurimbuka.
Mu buryo runaka, iyo abantu batangiye guhura n'ibibazo, bahita bibaza niba bashobora kwihanganira ibyo bibazo.
Elisabeth Ferrell, uhagarariye umuryango wita ku ndwara z'imbeba, yasabye abaturage bose gufasha.
Yagize ati "Dufite byinshi byo kwiga ku biremwa by'inyoni zo mu kirere, kandi ntituzi neza uko amoko menshi atubana agumaho".
Ronaldo yeguye ku birego byo gufata ku ngufu, mu gihe abanyamategeko be bahise bashinja ikinyamakuru cyo mu Budage
Cristiano Ronaldo yavuze ko ibyo aregwa ari "amakuru y'ibinyoma" kandi ko abakoze ibyo "bashaka kumenyekana" mu izina rye.
Biteguye no kurega ikinyamakuru cyo mu Budage cyitwa Der Spiegel, aho umwunganira mu mategeko amurega.
Umukinnyi w'imbere wa Portugal n'uwa Juventus, ashinjwa gusambanya ku ngufu umunyamerika witwa Kathryn Mayorga, mu 2009 i Las Vegas.
Nyuma yaho, bivugwa ko yamuhaye amadolari 375.000 kugira ngo akomeze ibanga ry'ibyabaye, nkuko Der Spiegel yabitangaje ku wa Gatanu.
Nyuma y'amasaha make asohotse, Ronaldo w'imyaka 33 yashyize video kuri Instagram, ahita ayishyira ku bakurikira miliyoni 142 kuri uru rubuga, avuga ko ibyo aregwa ari amakuru y'ibinyoma.
"Oya, oya, oya, oya, kandi oya.
"Ibyo navuze uyu munsi ni amakuru y'ibinyoma", ni ko umukinnyi wa FIFA watsindiye igihembo cya Ballon d'Or inshuro eshanu, yavuze imbere ya kamera.
Bashaka ko izina ryanjye rivugwa.
Ibyo ni ibisanzwe.
Ni abantu bakunda kuvuga izina ryanjye, ariko si ko bimeze mu mwuga wanjye.
"Ndi umuntu wishimye, kandi byose ni byiza", umukinnyi aravuga, aseka.
Abunganira Ronaldo mu mategeko barimo baritegura kugurisha ikinyamakuru Der Spiegel kubera ibirego by'uko ari "inyandiko idakwiriye ku birebana n'amakenga ku burenganzira bw'ibanga".
Umunyamategeko we Christian Schertz yavuze ko umukinnyi azasaba indishyi z'akababaro bitewe n'uburemere bw'iki cyaha, kikaba ari kimwe mu bikorwa bibi cyane by'ihohoterwa ry'uburenganzira bw'ikiremwamuntu mu myaka myinshi ishize".
Iki gitero cy'iterabwoba cyabaye muri Kamena 2009 mu cyumba cyo muri Palms Hotel na Casino i Las Vegas.
Nyuma yo guhurira mu nzu mberabyombi, bivugwa ko Ronaldo na Mayorga bagiye mu cyumba cy'umukinnyi wa Real Madrid, aho bivugwa ko yamusambanyije ku gahanga, nk'uko bivugwa n'inyandiko z'urukiko rw'akarere ka Clark County muri Nevada.
Mayorga yavuze ko Ronaldo yahanamye nyuma y'icyo cyaha, avuga ko 99 ku ijana ari umuntu mwiza, ariko ko yibeshya ku ijana".
Mu nyandiko zafashwe, haboneka ko Ronaldo yemereye uwo mugabo n'umugore ko bari baragiranye imibonano mpuzabitsina ariko nta kibazo.
Mayorda yavuze ko yagiye ku gipolisi, afata amafoto y'ibikomere bye mu bitaro, ariko nyuma y'aho agirana amasezerano n'urukiko kubera ko "yatinyaga ko abantu bazamwihorera, kandi afite ubwoba bwo kumukoza isoni mu ruhame".
Uyu mugore w'imyaka 34 yavuze ko ashaka gusubika amasezerano kubera ko agifite agahinda yatewe n'icyo gikorwa.
Igihe iki gitero cyabaga, Ronaldo yari mu nzira yo kuva muri Manchester United akajya muri Real Madrid, aho mu mpeshyi ishize yagiye mu ikipe ikomeye yo mu Butaliyani yitwa Juve mu mafaranga agera kuri miliyoni 100 z'ama-euro.
Brexit: Ubwongereza buzahora bwicuza kuba butarabona imodoka
Ubwongereza buzicuza iteka kuba bwaretse kuyobora imodoka nyuma ya Brexit, Minisitiri w'ubucuruzi Greg Clark yavuze.
Yavuze kandi ko "bihangayikishije" kuba Toyota UK yabwiye BBC ko mu gihe Ubwongereza buzaba buvuye mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'uburayi nta masezerano, izahagarika ibikorwa byayo mu ruganda rwayo ruri i Burnston, hafi ya Derby.
Clark yaravuze ati "dukeneye gushyira hamwe".
Uyu mucuruzi w'imodoka w'Umuyapani, yavuze ko gutinda kwishyura imisoro mu gihe cya Brexit nta masezerano afitanye n'u Buyapani, bishobora gutuma abantu batakaza akazi.
Uruganda rwa Burnston (rukora imodoka za Toyota Auris na Avensis) rwakoze imodoka zigera ku 150.000 umwaka ushize, 90% muri zo zagiye gutumizwa mu bindi bihugu bya EU.
"Tubona ko niba Ubwongereza buvuye mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'uburayi nta masezerano, mu mpera za Werurwe, umusaruro mu ruganda rwacu uzahagarikwa", niko Marvin Cook, umuyobozi wa Toyota i Burnston, yavuze.
Abandi bakoresha imodoka mu Bwongereza (urugero nka Honda, BMW na Jaguar Land Rover) na bo bagaragaje ko bafite ubwoba bw'uburyo ubucuruzi bw'imipaka buzakora mu gihe bavuye mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi nta masezerano.
Urugero, BMW yavuze ko izafunga uruganda rwayo rwa Mini mu gihe cy'ukwezi nyuma ya Brexit.
Impungenge nyinshi z'abakora imodoka ni uko bashobora guhura n'ibibazo byo gutakaza ibicuruzwa byabo mu gihe Brexit yaba nta masezerano.
Uruganda rwa Toyota ruri ku rwego rwo hejuru cyane, hamwe n'ibice biboneka mu minota 37 gusa, byaba mu Bwongereza cyangwa mu Burayi, ku modoka zikorerwa ku busabe.
Niba Ubwongereza buvuye mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi nta masezerano ku itariki ya 29 Werurwe, bishobora gutuma haba ibibazo ku mipaka, bigatuma haba ibitaramo byinshi kandi ibice bifatika bigahita biboneka.
Ntabwo bishoboka ko Toyota ibika ibikoresho birenze umunsi umwe mu ruganda rwa Derbyshire; kubwibyo, umusaruro ugomba guhagarikwa.
Clark yavuze ko gahunda ya Theresa May yiswe "Chequers" ku mishyikirano y'ejo hazaza y'ubumwe bw'u Burayi, "yashyizweho mu buryo butaziguye kugira ngo yirinde izo ngendo z'ubugenzuzi".
"Tugomba kugirana amasezerano, dushaka amasezerano meza cyane, atari ukugira ngo tuzabone intsinzi muri iki gihe gusa, ahubwo no kugira ngo tuzabone amahirwe mu gihe kizaza", ni ko yabwiye kuri BBC Radio 4 kuri Today.
Uretse Toyota, hari n'abandi bakora imodoka bagaragaje ko nta cyo bageraho mu gihe batagaragaje ko imigabane yabo y'ubucuruzi idashobora guhinduka.
Toyota ntabwo yashoboye kuvuga igihe ibi bihano bizamara, ariko iraburira ko mu gihe kirekire, ibiciro byongerewe bizatuma uruganda rutabasha guhatana, bityo imirimo igabanuke.
Peter Tsouvallaris, umukozi w'imyaka 24 muri Burnston, akaba n'umuhuzabikorwa w'uruganda rw'ishyirahamwe rya Unite, yavuze ko hari impungenge z'abanyamuryango.
Umuvugizi wa guverinoma yavuze ko "twasohoye igishushanyo mbonera gifatika kandi cyumvikana cy'imishyikirano y'igihe kizaza n'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi".
Mu biro by'umukuru w'igihugu, bavuga ko inama ya Trump na Rosenstein ishobora kongera gusubikwa.
Inama y'ingenzi hagati ya Donald Trump n'umushinjacyaha mukuru wungirije Rod Rosenstein ishobora gusubikwa n'ikindi cyumweru, mu gihe amakimbirane akomeje ku byerekeye Brett Kavanaugh, umukandida w'Urukiko rw'Ikirenga, nkuko byatangajwe n'ibiro bya perezida w'Amerika, White House, ku cyumweru.
Rosenstein agenzura akazi k'umujyanama wihariye Robert Mueller, Mueller arimo akora iperereza ku ruhare rw'Uburusiya mu matora ya Amerika, isano hagati y'abafasha ba Trump n'Uburusiya, ndetse n'ibyaha by'ubugizi bwa nabi by'umukuru w'igihugu.
Kuba Trump yarirukanye umushinjacyaha mukuru wungirije, bishobora gushyira mu kaga ubwigenge bwa Mueller, byavuzwe cyane muri Washington mu mezi ashize.
Mu ntangiriro z'uku kwezi, ikinyamakuru New York Times cyatangaje ko Rosenstein yatekereje kwambara micro mu ibanga kugira ngo ashobore gufata amajwi y'ibiganiro bye na Trump, ndetse no gukura perezida ku butegetsi hakurikijwe ingingo ya 25 y'itegeko nshinga rya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
Rosenstein yahakanye ibyo yari azi.
Ariko kandi, ku wa mbere w'icyumweru gishize, yagiye mu biro bya White House, mu gihe hari amakuru yavugaga ko agiye kwegura.
Ahubwo, yatangaje ko azagirana inama na Trump kuwa kane w'iki cyumweru, ubu akaba ari ku cyicaro cya ONU i New York.
Trump yavuze ko atifuzaga kwirukana Rosenstein, ariko nyuma yaje gusubika iyo nama kubera gutinya guhangana na komite ishinzwe ubutabera muri Sena, aho Kavanaugh n'umwe mu bagore bamushinje ihohoterwa rishingiye ku gitsina, Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, batanze ubuhamya.
Ku wa Gatanu, Perezida Trump yasabye FBI gukora iperereza ry'icyumweru cyose ku birego bya Kavanaugh, bituma amatora yo muri Sena asubikwa.
Sarah Sanders, umujyanama wa Trump mu itangazamakuru, yagaragaye kuri Fox News ku Cyumweru.
Abajijwe ku nama na Rosenstein, yagize ati "Nta tariki iteganyijwe; ishobora kuba muri iki cyumweru, ariko nshobora kumva ko ishobora gusubikwa mu kindi cyumweru, urebye ibibera mu Rukiko rw'Ikirenga.
Ariko tuzabireba, kuko buri gihe nkunda kubwira itangazamakuru".
Hari abanyamakuru batabyemera kuko Sanders nta kiganiro yagiranye n'itangazamakuru kuva ku itariki ya 10 Nzeri.
Uwari uhagarariye ikiganiro cya Chris Wallace yamubajije impamvu yahunze.
Sanders yavuze ko kuba nta biganiro by'abanyamakuru byabaye, atari ukubera ko abanyamakuru ba televiziyo "bibonaga ko bafite agaciro", ahubwo ko "yemera ko bafite agaciro".
Nyuma yaho, yavuze ko Trump azajya agirana ibiganiro n'itangazamakuru.
Yagize ati "Perezida akora ibiganiro byinshi by'ibibazo n'ibisubizo kurusha abamusimbuye", yongeraho atavuze ibimenyetso, ati "Twagenzuye iyo mibare".
Sanders yavuze ko bazakomeza kugira inama z'abanyamakuru, ariko niba abanyamakuru bashobora kubaza ibibazo Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, byaba ari byiza cyane kuruta ko bambaza.
Ibyo twagerageje kubikora kenshi, kandi mwabibonye kenshi mu byumweru bishize, kandi bizasimbura ikiganiro n'abanyamakuru, ubwo tuzaba tugiye kuvugana na Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika".
Trump asubiza ibibazo kenshi iyo avuye mu biro bye, mu biganiro bye n'abanyamakuru mu gihe hari abategetsi b'ibihugu.
Ubusanzwe nta nama y'abanyamakuru aba yagiriye.
Impamvu zishoboka y'ibyo, Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yabigaragaje mu buryo budasanzwe, ndetse rimwe na rimwe mu buryo budasanzwe, ubwo yagaragaraga imbere y'abanyamakuru bari bateraniye i New York muri iki cyumweru.
Umunyamabanga ushinzwe ubuzima mu Bwongereza yandikiye abakozi b'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'uburayi bakorera muri NHS yo muri Scotland, avuga ko bafite impungenge ku bijyanye na Brexit.
Umunyamabanga ushinzwe ubuzima yandikiye abakozi bo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'uburayi bakorera mu kigo nderabuzima cya NHS mu gihugu cya Scotland, abishimira mu izina ry'igihugu cyose, abasaba kuguma muri icyo kigo nyuma ya Brexit.
Mu ibaruwa yanditswe n'umushingamateka wo muri Scotland witwa Jeane Freeman, yavuze ko hasigaye amezi atandatu ngo Ubwongereza buve mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi.
Leta ya Ecosse yamaze kwemera kwishyura amafaranga y'abakozi b'ibihugu by'i Burayi bakora mu nzego za Leta, kugira ngo babone uburenganzira bwo kuba mu gihugu cyabo.
Mu ibaruwa Freeman yanditse yagize ati "Mu gihe cy'impeshyi, ibiganiro bya Brexit byagiye bigenda neza hagati y'Ubwongereza n'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, kandi byitezwe ko hari umwanzuro ufatwa mu itumba.
Icyakora, leta y'Ubwongereza yongeye imbaraga mu kwitegura uko byagenda kose kugira ngo igihugu kive muri uyu muryango nta masezerano.
Ndabizi ko ibi ari ibihe bikomeye kuri mwese.
Ni yo mpamvu nifuzaga kubamenyesha ko buri mukozi wese ahabwa agaciro, uko yaba ari kose.
Abakozi bacu bo muri EU ndetse n'abo hanze batanga ubumenyi n'ubumenyi bw'ingirakamaro, bigatuma serivisi z'ubuzima zirushaho gukora neza, ku nyungu z'abarwayi n'imiryango dukorera.
Ecosse ni iwawe nta gushidikanya, kandi twiteze ko muzahora muri kumwe natwe".
Christion Abercrombie yafashwe mu buryo bwihutirwa nyuma yo gukomereka mu mutwe.
Umunyezamu Christion Abercrombie wa Tennessee State Tigers yahawe ubuvuzi bwihutirwa nyuma yo gukomereka mu mutwe nyuma yo gutsindwa 31-27 n'ikipe ya Vanderbilt Commodores ku wa Gatandatu, nkuko byatangajwe na Mike Organ wa Tennessee.
Umutoza mukuru wa Tennessee State, Rod Reed, yavuze ko umukinnyi wa Tennessee, James Brown, yahuye n'ikosa mu mutwe mbere gato y'umukino wo kwishyura.
Reed yavuze ko "yaguye mu muhanda maze ahita asama".
Abatoza n'abaganga batanze umwuka wa ogisijeni kuri Abercrombie aho mu itsinda, bamushyira mu cyumba cyo kuryamamo kugira ngo amukurikirane.
Umuvugizi w'ikipe ya Tennessee State yabwiye Chris Harris kuri WSMV i Nashville, Tennessee ko uyu mugabo amaze kubagwa kandi ko ari mu bitaro bya Vanderbilt Medical Center.
Harris yavuze ko nta makuru arambuye y'ubwoko bw'imvune cyangwa uburemere bwayo, kandi ko ikipe ya Tennessee State ikomeje kugerageza kumenya igihe iyo mvune yabereye.
Ubu ari mu mwaka we wa kabiri mu ikipe ya Abercrombie Red Shirts, ndetse ni na we mwaka we wa mbere mu ikipe ya Tennessee State kuva yajya muri Illinois.
Yatsinze ibitego bitanu mbere yo kuva mu mukino wo ku wa gatandatu, bituma atsinda ibitego 18 muri uyu mwaka wose.
Abaguzi b'abanyamahanga bagomba kwishyura umusoro wo hejuru ku mpuruza igihe bagura umutungo mu Bwongereza
Abaguzi b'abanyamahanga bazishyura umusoro w'inyongera ku mafaranga y'ibiro igihe bazagura umutungo mu Bwongereza, kandi ayo mafaranga y'inyongera azakoreshwa mu gufasha abantu batagira aho baba, hakurikijwe gahunda z'ishyaka rya Conservative.
Ni uburyo bwo kwamagana intsinzi ya Corbyn mu gukangurira abatora bato.
Mu Bwongereza, imisoro ku byuma by'amatara yiyongera ku bantu batishyura imisoro.
Ikigega cy'imari cyatangaje ko ibyo bizatuma haboneka izindi miriyoni 120 z'amapawundi ku mwaka, mu gufasha abatagira aho baba.
Abaguzi b'abanyamahanga bazishyura umusoro w'inyongera ku mafaranga y'inyongera igihe bazagura umutungo mu Bwongereza, kandi ayo mafaranga y'inyongera azakoreshwa mu gufasha abantu batagira aho baba, nk'uko Theresa May yabitangaje uyu munsi.
Ubu buryo bwa Corbyn bugamije kwamagana intsinzi afite mu gukwepa abatoza bato, binyuze mu gutanga amasezerano yo gutanga amazu ku giciro cyiza no kwishyura imisoro myinshi ku bafite amafaranga menshi.
Umusoro ku mpeta uzongererwa abantu n'ibigo bidatanga imisoro mu Bwongereza, kandi amafaranga y'inyongera yakusanyijwe azakoreshwa mu bikorwa bya leta byo kugabanya abantu barara mu muhanda.
