Umushinjacyaha mukuru w'igihugu arashaka igihano cy'urupfu ku muntu ukekwaho kuba ari we wateje ibitero by'iterabwoba i New York.
Umushinjacyaha wa leta y'i New York arashaka igihano cy'urupfu kuri Sayfullo Saipov ukekwaho kuba ariwe wagabye igitero cy'iterabwoba mu mujyi wa New York cyahitanye abantu umunani. Igihano nk'icyo cyaherukaga gutangwa muri leta ku cyaha cya leta kuva mu 1953.
Bivugwa ko Saipov w'imyaka 30 yakoresheje ikamyo yari yakodesheje mu nzu y'ubucuruzi ya Home Depot mu gitero yakoze ku muhanda wa West Side Highway mu majyepfo ya Manhattan, mu gitero cyo mu kwezi kwa cumi, yatwaye abagenzi n'amagare bose imbere.
Kugira ngo urubanza rw'urupfu rufatwe nk'impamvu, umushinjacyaha agomba kugaragaza ko Saipov yishe abo bantu umunani abigambiriye kandi akomeretsa abandi benshi cyane, nk'uko bivugwa mu nyandiko y'abacamanza y'itegeko ry'urupfu yashyikirijwe Urukiko rw'Ibanze rw'Akarere k'Amajyepfo ka New York.
Dukurikije inyandiko z'amategeko, mu bihe byombi igihano cy'urupfu gishobora gutangwa.
Nyuma y'ibyumweru bike gusa iki gitero kibaye, urukiko rw'ubujurire rwa leta rwahamije Saipov ibyaha 22 birimo ibyaha umunani by'ubwicanyi, ibyo biro bikunze gukoresha mu kuregera ibyaha by'ubugizi bwa nabi, n'icyaha kimwe cy'urugomo n'ubwicanyi mu modoka.
Ubushinjacyaha bwavuze ko icyo gitero cyagombaga kuba cyaratekerejweho kandi gitegurwa neza, kuko Saipov yacyise "ubugome".
Ibikorwa bya Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov byateje ibikomere, kwangirika no gutakaza imiryango n'incuti z'abantu bakurikira: Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza na Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, nk'uko bigaragara mu butumwa bw'imigambi.
Batanu mu bapfuye bari ba mukerarugendo bo muri Argentine.
Hashize imyaka igera ku icumi, uhereye igihe Akarere k'Amajyepfo ka New York kaherukaga kwakira urubanza rw'igihano cy'urupfu.
Icyo gihe, ushinjwa Khalid Barnes yahamijwe icyaha cyo kwica abacuruzaga ibiyobyabwenge babiri, ariko amaherezo muri Nzeri 2009, yakatiwe gufungwa burundu.
Igihe cya nyuma igihano cy'urupfu cyatanzwe mu rubanza rw'igihugu cya New York cyari mu 1953 ubwo cyahanishwaga Julius na Ethel Rosenberg, bashinjwaga kugambanira Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Abasoviyeti mu gihe cy'Intambara y'Ubutita imyaka ibiri mbere yaho.
Abavandimwe ba Rosenberg baciriwe urwo gupfa ku ntebe y'umuriro ku itariki ya 19 Kamena 1953.
Ibaruwa y'ubutabera igaragaza ko Saipov, umuturage wa Uzbekistan, nta cyo yagaragaje cyo kwicuza mu minsi n'amezi yakurikiye igitero.
Polisi yavuze ko nta kintu na kimwe yabwiye abacamanza cyatumye yumva ababajwe n'ibyo yakoze.
Iyo raporo ivuga ko Saipov yabwiye abategetsi ko igitero cyatewe n'amashusho ya ISIS yari kuri telefoni ye.
Polisi ivuga ko uwo mugabo yasabye ko ibendera rya ISIS rishyirwa mu cyumba cye cy'ibitaro.
Yatangaje ko ari umwere ku birego 22 byose.
David Patton, umwe mu bashinzwe ubutabera muri leta zunze ubumwe z'Amerika, ushinzwe gusimbura Saipov, yavuze ko "bacitse intege cyane" n'icyemezo cy'ubushinjacyaha.
"Twumva ko icyemezo cyo gusaba igihano cy'urupfu aho kwemera icyaha cyo gufungwa burundu nta burenganzira bwo kurekurwa, kizakomeza gusa ibikomere by'abantu bagizweho ingaruka n'ibi bintu", ni ko Patton yavuze.
Abunganira Saipov basabye umushinjacyaha kubanza kwirinda gutanga igihano cy'urupfu.
