Patrick Dwyer yatsinze ibitego bibiri bya Giants kuri Dundee
Dundee Stars kuri uyu wa Gatandatu yongeye gutsinda umukino wo mu cyiciro cya mbere yatsinzwe na Belfast Giants ku wa Gatanu, itsinda 5-3 umukino wa kabiri wahitanywe i Dundee.
Giants yatangiye umukino itsinze ibitego bibiri bya Patrick Dwyer na Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan na Jordan Cownie batumye ibintu birangira nta cyo bitwaye, ariko bidatinze Giants yongeye kubigiramo uruhare.
Francois Bouchard yongeye guhangana na Dundee, amaherezo yatsindiwe ibitego bibiri bya Lukas Lundvald Nielsen.
