Umukinnyi wa mbere Dwyer yaje ku munota wa kane, saa 3:35 am, afashijwe na Kendall McFaull, nyuma y'iminota ine, David Rutherford afasha Beauvillier, maze yongera igitego inshuro ebyiri.
