Mu gice cya kabiri, Cownie na Charles Corcoran bafatanyije gufasha Nielsen no guha Dundee ubuyobozi bwa mbere muri uyu mukino, kandi mu gice cya nyuma, igitego cya gatanu hamwe nacyo byateye ikipe gutsinda.
