Impamvu intambara y'ubucuruzi hagati y'Amerika n'Ubushinwa ishobora kugirira akamaro Beijing
Ibi byatangaje ko intambara y'ubucuruzi hagati y'Ubushinwa na Amerika yatangiye. Nubwo intambara ikomeje kuba ikomeye, abahanga bavuga ko kuba ibihugu byombi byatandukanye bishobora kugirira akamaro u Bushinwa.
Perezida Donald Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yatanze ubutumwa bwa mbere mu ntangiriro z'uyu mwaka, ubwo yashyiraga umusoro ku bicuruzwa by'ingenzi Ubushinwa bwangizaga, birimo ibikoresho by'izuba, ibyuma na aluminiyumu.
Inyongera ikomeye cyane y'ibi biciro yageze muri iki cyumweru, ubwo ibiciro bishya by'ibicuruzwa bifite agaciro ka miliyari 200 z'amadolari (150million pounds) byatangwaga ku kigero cya kimwe cya kabiri cy'ibicuruzwa byose biva mu Bushinwa bijyanwa muri Amerika.
U Bushinwa bwamaze kwihorera buri gihe, bwaherukaga kuzamura ibiciro bya 5% na 10% ku bicuruzwa bya Amerika bifite agaciro ka miliyari 60 z'amadolari.
Ubushinwa bwavuze ko buzahangana n'iterambere rya Amerika, kandi ubukungu bwa kabiri ku isi ntibuzahindura ibitekerezo byayo mu buryo bworoshye.
Gusaba Washington guhagarika ibiganiro bishobora gutuma umuntu akurikiranwa n'ubutabera, ariko kwemera ku mugaragaro Amerika byaba ari ugusebya Perezida w'u Bushinwa Xi Jinping.
Ariko kandi, abahanga bavuga ko niba Beijing ikora neza, ingufu z'intambara y'ubucuruzi z'Amerika zishobora kugirira akamaro u Bushinwa mu gihe kirekire, ku buryo bugabanya ubudahangarwa hagati y'ubukungu bw'ibihugu byombi.
"Kugira ngo abanyapolitiki b'i Washington cyangwa i Beijing bahite bafata icyemezo, bishobora gutuma mu bihugu byombi haba imvururu z'ubukungu, ibintu biteje akaga kurusha uko abahanga babitekerezaga", niko umushakashatsi witwa Abigail Grace, ukorana n'abandi bashakashatsi mu by'Aziya mu kigo cy'umutekano gishya cya Amerika, yavuze.
Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga ya Syria yatangaje ko yiteguye kwakira impunzi z'Abasiriya zisubiye iwabo.
Syria ivuga ko yiteguye kwakira impunzi zashaka gutaha ku bushake, kandi irasaba ubufasha mu kongera kubaka igihugu cyasenywe n'intambara imaze imyaka irenga irindwi.
Mu ijambo yagejeje ku Nteko Rusange y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga wa Repubulika ya Kongo, Walid al-Moualem, yavuze ko ibintu mu gihugu birimo birushaho kuba byiza.
Yagize ati "Uyu munsi, ibintu muri ako gace birakomeye kandi bifite umutekano, kubera iterambere ryagezweho mu kurwanya iterabwoba".
Leta ikomeje ibikorwa byo gusana imirima y'ibyatsi byangijwe n'ibyihebe, kugira ngo abantu basubire mu buzima busanzwe vuba bishoboka.
Ubu, ibintu bimeze neza ku mpunzi zigerageza gutaha ku bushake mu bihugu zataye kubera iterabwoba n'ingamba z'ubukungu zituma ubuzima bwabo bwa buri munsi bugorana.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye rivuga ko abantu barenga miliyoni 5.5 bahunze igihugu cyabo kuva intambara yatangira mu 2011.
Abandi bantu bagera kuri miriyoni esheshatu baba muri icyo gihugu bakeneye ubufasha bw'ubuntu.
Al-Moualem yavuze ko ubutegetsi bwa Siriya bushimira cyane ubufasha bwo kongera kubaka igihugu cyabaye amatongo.
Ariko yavuze ko atazemera ubufasha ubwo ari bwo bwose bufite imimerere, cyangwa se ubufasha ubwo ari bwo bwose buturuka mu bihugu byashyigikiye iyo myigaragambyo.
Uburayi bwatsinze igikombe cya Ryder Cup i Paris
Nyuma yo gutsinda ikipe y'Amerika ku manota 10.5 ku manota 16.5 ku munota wa nyuma, ikipe y'u Burayi yegukanye igikombe cya Ryder Cup cya 2018 cyabereye kuri Le Golf National hanze ya Paris mu Bufaransa.
Amerika yatsinzwe inshuro esheshatu zikurikirana ku butaka bw'i Burayi, kandi ntiyari yarigeze itsindira igikombe cya Ryder mu Burayi kuva mu 1993.
Uburayi bwongeye kwegukana ikamba ubwo ikipe yari iyobowe na Kapiteni Thomas Bjorn wo muri Danemark yatsindaga Amerika ku manota 14.5.
Phil Mickelson wo muri Amerika yagize ibihe bibi hafi ya byose muri iri rushanwa, aterera igitego cyo kwishyura mu mazi ku cyobo cya 16 mu gice cya 3, ahita acyaha Francesco Molinari.
Umukinnyi w'umukino wa golf w'Umutaliyani Milinari yahagaze cyane muri buri gice, kandi yabaye umwe mu bakinnyi bane bigeze bagera ku 5, 0 na 0 kuva imiterere y'irushanwa ryatangiye mu 1979.
Umunyamerika Jordan Spieth yatsinze ibitego 5-4 maze atsindwa umukinnyi mubi cyane mu ikipe y'i Burayi, Thorbjorn Olesen wo muri Danemark.
Umukinnyi w'umupira w'amaguru ukomeye ku isi Dustin Johnson yatsinze umukinnyi wo mu Bwongereza Ian Poulter ibitego 2-1 maze agera ku mukino wa nyuma w'igikombe cya Ryder.
Umunya-Espagne Sergio García, witabiriye ibikombe umunani bya Ryder Cup, yabaye umukinnyi w'ibanze w'i Burayi watsinze iri rushanwa, afite amanota 25,5.
